name: Pound
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 긴 꼬리나 손 등을 사용하여 상대를 때려서 공격한다.

name: Karate Chop
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move.
effect_entry_ko: 날카로운 당수로 상대를 때려서 공격한다. 급소에 맞기 쉽다.

name: Double Slap
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits 2–5 times in one turn. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use.
effect_entry_ko: 연속 뺨치기로 상대를 때려서 공격한다. 2-5회 동안 연속으로 쓴다.

name: Comet Punch
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits 2–5 times in one turn. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use.
effect_entry_ko: 노도 같은 펀치로 상대를 세게 때려서 공격한다. 2-5회 동안 연속으로 쓴다.

name: Mega Punch
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 힘을 담은 펀치로 상대를 공격한다.

name: Pay Day
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. After the battle ends, the winner receives five times the user's level in extra money for each time this move was used.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 몸에 돈을 세게 던져서 공격한다. 배틀 후에 돈을 받을 수 있다.

name: Fire Punch
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to burn the target.
effect_entry_ko: 불꽃을 담은 펀치로 상대를 공격한다. 화상 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Ice Punch
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to freeze the target.
effect_entry_ko: 냉기를 담은 펀치로 상대를 공격한다. 얼음 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Thunder Punch
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to paralyze the target.
effect_entry_ko: 전격을 담은 펀치로 상대를 공격한다. 마비 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Scratch
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 단단하고 뾰족한 날카로운 손톱으로 상대를 할퀴어서 공격한다.

name: Vise Grip
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 상대를 양쪽에서 집어서 데미지를 준다.

name: Guillotine
effect_entry: Inflicts damage equal to the target's max HP. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers. This move's accuracy is 30% plus 1% for each level the user is higher than the target. If the user is a lower level than the target, this move will fail. Because this move inflicts a specific and finite amount of damage, endure still prevents the target from fainting. The effects of lock on, mind reader, and no guard still apply, as long as the user is equal or higher level than the target. However, they will not give this move a chance to break through detect or protect.
effect_entry_ko: 큰 집게로 상대를 베어 갈라 공격한다. 맞으면 일격에 기절한다.

name: Razor Wind
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move. User charges for one turn before attacking. This move cannot be selected by sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 바람의 칼날을 만들어 2턴째에 상대를 공격한다. 급소에 맞기 쉽다.

name: Swords Dance
effect_entry: Raises the user's Attack by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 싸움의 춤을 격렬하게 추며 기세를 높인다. 자신의 공격을 크게 올린다.

name: Cut
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 낫이나 발톱 등으로 상대를 베어 공격한다. 가느다란 나무도 자를 수 있다.

name: Gust
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target is under the effect of bounce, fly, or sky drop, this move will hit with double power.
effect_entry_ko: 날개로 일으킨 격한 바람을 상대에게 부딪쳐서 공격한다.

name: Wing Attack
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 크게 펼친 훌륭한 날개를 상대에게 부딪쳐서 공격한다.

name: Whirlwind
effect_entry: Switches the target out for another of its trainer's Pokémon selected at random. Wild battles end immediately. Doesn't affect Pokémon with suction cups or under the effect of ingrain.
effect_entry_ko: 상대를 날려버려서 교대할 포켓몬을 끌어낸다. 야생의 경우에는 배틀이 끝난다.

name: Fly
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User flies high into the air for one turn, becoming immune to attack, and hits on the second turn. During the immune turn, gust, hurricane, sky uppercut, smack down, thunder, twister, and whirlwind still hit the user normally. gust and twister also have double power against the user. The damage from hail and sandstorm still applies during the immune turn. The user may be hit during its immune turn if under the effect of lock on, mind reader, or no guard. This move cannot be used while gravity is in effect. This move cannot be selected by sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 1턴째에 하늘을 날아 2턴째에 상대를 공격한다. 알고 있는 도시로 날아갈 수 있다.

name: Bind
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. For the next 2–5 turns, the target cannot leave the field and is damaged for 1/16 its max HP at the end of each turn. The user continues to use other moves during this time. If the user leaves the field, this effect ends. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use. rapid spin cancels this effect.
effect_entry_ko: 긴 몸이나 덩굴 등을 써서 4-5턴 동안 상대를 조여 공격한다.

name: Slam
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 긴 꼬리나 덩굴 등을 사용해 상대를 힘껏 쳐서 공격한다.

name: Vine Whip
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 채찍처럼 휘어지는 가늘고 긴 덩굴로 상대를 힘껏 쳐서 공격한다.

name: Stomp
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to make the target flinch. Power is doubled against Pokémon that have used minimize since entering the field.
effect_entry_ko: 큰 발로 상대를 짓밟아서 공격한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: Double Kick
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits twice in one turn.
effect_entry_ko: 2개의 다리로 상대를 걷어차서 공격한다. 2회 연속으로 데미지를 준다.

name: Mega Kick
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 굉장한 힘을 담은 킥으로 상대를 걷어차서 공격한다.

name: Jump Kick
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If this move misses, is blocked by protect or detect, or has no effect, the user takes damage equal to half of its max HP rounded down. This move cannot be used while gravity is in effect.
effect_entry_ko: 높이 점프해서 킥으로 상대를 공격한다. 빗나가면 자신이 데미지를 입는다.

name: Rolling Kick
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 몸을 재빨리 회전시키며 걷어차서 공격한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: Sand Attack
effect_entry: Lowers the target's accuracy by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 얼굴에 모래를 뿌려서 명중률을 떨어뜨린다.

name: Headbutt
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 머리를 내밀어 곧장 돌진하여 공격한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: Horn Attack
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 날카롭고 뾰족한 뿔로 상대를 공격한다.

name: Fury Attack
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits 2–5 times in one turn. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use.
effect_entry_ko: 뿔이나 부리로 상대를 찔러서 공격한다. 2-5회 동안 연속으로 쓴다.

name: Horn Drill
effect_entry: Inflicts damage equal to the target's max HP. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers. This move's accuracy is 30% plus 1% for each level the user is higher than the target. If the user is a lower level than the target, this move will fail. Because this move inflicts a specific and finite amount of damage, endure still prevents the target from fainting. The effects of lock on, mind reader, and no guard still apply, as long as the user is equal or higher level than the target. However, they will not give this move a chance to break through detect or protect.
effect_entry_ko: 회전하는 뿔을 상대에게 꿰찔러서 공격한다. 맞으면 일격에 기절한다.

name: Tackle
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 상대를 향해서 몸 전체를 부딪쳐가며 공격한다.

name: Body Slam
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to paralyze the target.
effect_entry_ko: 몸 전체로 상대를 덮쳐 눌러 공격한다. 마비 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Wrap
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. For the next 2–5 turns, the target cannot leave the field and is damaged for 1/16 its max HP at the end of each turn. The user continues to use other moves during this time. If the user leaves the field, this effect ends. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use. rapid spin cancels this effect.
effect_entry_ko: 긴 몸이나 덩굴 등을 사용해 4-5턴 동안 상대를 휘감아 공격한다.

name: Take Down
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User takes 1/4 the damage it inflicts in recoil.
effect_entry_ko: 굉장한 기세로 상대에게 부딪쳐 공격한다. 자신도 조금 데미지를 입는다.

name: Thrash
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User is forced to attack with this move for 2–3 turns,selected at random. After the last hit, the user becomes confused. safeguard does not protect against the confusion from this move.
effect_entry_ko: 2-3턴 동안 마구 난동 부려서 상대를 공격한다. 난동 부린 뒤에는 혼란에 빠진다.

name: Double-Edge
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User takes 1/3 the damage it inflicts in recoil.
effect_entry_ko: 목숨을 걸고 상대에게 돌진하여 공격을 한다. 자신도 상당한 데미지를 입는다.

name: Tail Whip
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 꼬리를 좌우로 귀엽게 흔들어 방심을 유도한다. 상대의 방어를 떨어뜨린다.

name: Poison Sting
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to poison the target.
effect_entry_ko: 독이 있는 침을 상대에게 꿰찔러서 공격한다. 독 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Twineedle
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits twice in the same turn. Has a 20% chance to poison the target.
effect_entry_ko: 2개의 침을 상대에게 꿰찔러 2회 연속으로 데미지를 준다. 독 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Pin Missile
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits 2–5 times in one turn. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use.
effect_entry_ko: 날카로운 침을 상대에게 발사해서 공격한다. 2-5회 동안 연속으로 쓴다.

name: Leer
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 날카로운 눈초리로 겁을 주어 상대의 방어를 떨어뜨린다.

name: Bite
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 날카롭고 뾰족한 이빨로 물어서 공격한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: Growl
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Attack by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 귀여운 울음소리를 들려주고 관심을 끌어 방심한 사이에 상대의 공격을 떨어뜨린다.

name: Roar
effect_entry: Switches the target out for another of its trainer's Pokémon selected at random. Wild battles end immediately. Doesn't affect Pokémon with suction cups or under the effect of ingrain.
effect_entry_ko: 상대를 도망가게 해서 교대할 포켓몬을 끌어낸다. 야생의 경우에는 배틀이 끝난다.

name: Sing
effect_entry: Puts the target to sleep.
effect_entry_ko: 기분 좋은 예쁜 노랫소리를 들려주고 상대를 잠듦 상태로 만든다.

name: Supersonic
effect_entry: Confuses the target.
effect_entry_ko: 특수한 음파를 몸에서 발산하여 상대를 혼란시킨다.

name: Sonic Boom
effect_entry: Inflicts exactly 20 damage.
effect_entry_ko: 충격파를 상대에 부딪쳐서 공격한다. 언제나 20의 데미지를 준다.

name: Disable
effect_entry: Disables the target's last used move, preventing its use for 4–7 turns, selected at random, or until the target leaves the field. If the target hasn't used a move since entering the field, if it tried to use a move this turn and failed, if its last used move has 0 PP remaining, or if it already has a move disabled, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 움직임을 막아 바로 전에 쓴 기술을 4턴 동안 사용할 수 없게 만든다.

name: Acid
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to lower the target's Special Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 강한 산을 상대에게 끼얹어 공격한다. 상대의 특수방어를 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Ember
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to burn the target.
effect_entry_ko: 작은 불꽃을 상대에게 발사하여 공격한다. 화상 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Flamethrower
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to burn the target.
effect_entry_ko: 세찬 불꽃을 상대에게 발사하여 공격한다. 화상 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Mist
effect_entry: Pokémon on the user's side of the field are immune to stat-lowering effects for five turns. guard swap, heart swap, and power swap may still be used. defog used by an opponent will end this effect.
effect_entry_ko: 하얀 안개로 몸을 덮는다. 5턴 동안 상대에 의해 능력이 떨어지지 않게 된다.

name: Water Gun
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 물을 기세 좋게 상대에게 발사하여 공격한다.

name: Hydro Pump
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 대량의 물을 세찬 기세로 상대에게 발사하여 공격한다.

name: Surf
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target is in the first turn of dive, this move will hit with double power.
effect_entry_ko: 큰 파도로 자신의 주위에 있는 포켓몬을 공격한다. 물 위도 헤엄쳐서 나아간다.

name: Ice Beam
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to freeze the target.
effect_entry_ko: 냉동빔을 상대에게 발사하여 공격한다. 얼음 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Blizzard
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to freeze the target. During hail, this move has 100% accuracy. It also has a (100 - accuracy)% chance to break through the protection of protect and detect.
effect_entry_ko: 세찬 눈보라를 상대에게 내뿜어 공격한다. 얼음 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Psybeam
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to confuse the target.
effect_entry_ko: 이상한 광선을 상대에게 발사하여 공격한다. 혼란시킬 때가 있다.

name: Bubble Beam
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to lower the target's Speed by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 거품을 기세 좋게 상대에게 발사하여 공격한다. 스피드를 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Aurora Beam
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to lower the target's Attack by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 무지개색의 빔을 상대에게 발사하여 공격한다. 공격을 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Hyper Beam
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User loses its next turn to "recharge", and cannot attack or switch out during that turn.
effect_entry_ko: 강한 광선을 상대에게 발사하여 공격한다. 다음 턴은 움직일 수 없다.

name: Peck
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 날카롭고 뾰족한 부리나 뿔로 상대를 쪼아서 공격한다.

name: Drill Peck
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 회전하면서 뾰족한 부리를 상대에게 꿰찔러 공격한다.

name: Submission
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User takes 1/4 the damage it inflicts in recoil.
effect_entry_ko: 땅에 자신과 함께 상대를 내던져 공격한다. 자신도 조금 데미지를 입는다.

name: Low Kick
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power increases with the target's weight in kilograms, to a maximum of 120. Target's weight | Power --------------- | ----: Up to 10kg   |  20 Up to 25kg   |  40 Up to 50kg   |  60 Up to 100kg   |  80 Up to 200kg   |  100 Above 200kg   |  120
effect_entry_ko: 발을 강하게 걸고 상대를 넘어뜨려 공격한다. 상대가 무거울수록 위력이 올라간다.

name: Counter
effect_entry: Targets the last opposing Pokémon to hit the user with a physical move this turn. Inflicts twice the damage that move did to the user. If there is no eligible target, this move will fail. Type immunity applies, but other type effects are ignored. This move cannot be copied by mirror move, nor selected by assist or metronome.
effect_entry_ko: 상대로부터 받은 물리공격의 데미지를 2배로 만들어 같은 상대에게 돌려준다.

name: Seismic Toss
effect_entry: Inflicts damage equal to the user's level. Type immunity applies, but other type effects are ignored.
effect_entry_ko: 인력을 사용해 내던진다. 자신의 레벨과 똑같은 데미지를 상대에게 준다.

name: Strength
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 혼신의 힘으로 상대를 세게 때려서 공격한다. 무거운 돌을 밀 수도 있다.

name: Absorb
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Drains half the damage inflicted to heal the user.
effect_entry_ko: 양분을 흡수하여 공격한다. 상대에게 입힌 데미지의 절반에 해당하는 HP를 회복할 수 있다.

name: Mega Drain
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Drains half the damage inflicted to heal the user.
effect_entry_ko: 양분을 흡수하여 공격한다. 상대에게 입힌 데미지의 절반에 해당하는 HP를 회복할 수 있다.

name: Leech Seed
effect_entry: Plants a seed on the target that drains 1/8 of its max HP at the end of every turn and heals the user for the amount taken. Has no effect on grass Pokémon. The seed remains until the target leaves the field. The user takes damage instead of being healed if the target has liquid ooze. rapid spin will remove this effect. This effect is passed on by baton pass.
effect_entry_ko: 씨가 뿌려진 상대의 HP를 매 턴 조금씩 흡수하여 자신의 HP를 회복한다.

name: Growth
effect_entry: Raises the user's Attack and Special Attack by one stage each. During sunny day, raises both stats by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 몸을 일시에 크게 성장시켜 공격과 특수공격을 올린다.

name: Razor Leaf
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move.
effect_entry_ko: 잎사귀를 날려 상대를 베어 공격한다. 급소에 맞기 쉽다.

name: Solar Beam
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User charges for one turn before attacking. During sunny day, the charge turn is skipped. During hail, rain dance, or sandstorm, power is halved. This move cannot be selected by sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 1턴째에 빛을 가득 모아 2턴째에 빛의 다발을 발사하여 공격한다.

name: Poison Powder
effect_entry: Poisons the target.
effect_entry_ko: 독이 있는 가루를 많이 흩뿌려서 상대를 독 상태로 만든다.

name: Stun Spore
effect_entry: Paralyzes the target.
effect_entry_ko: 저리 가루를 많이 흩뿌려서 상대를 마비 상태로 만든다.

name: Sleep Powder
effect_entry: Puts the target to sleep.
effect_entry_ko: 잠이 오는 가루를 많이 흩뿌려서 상대를 잠듦 상태로 만든다.

name: Petal Dance
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User is forced to attack with this move for 2–3 turns,selected at random. After the last hit, the user becomes confused. safeguard does not protect against the confusion from this move.
effect_entry_ko: 2-3턴 동안 꽃을 흩뿌려서 상대를 공격한다. 흩뿌린 뒤에는 혼란에 빠진다.

name: String Shot
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Speed by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 입에서 뿜어낸 실을 휘감아서 상대의 스피드를 크게 떨어뜨린다.

name: Dragon Rage
effect_entry: Inflicts exactly 40 damage.
effect_entry_ko: 분노의 충격파를 상대에게 부딪쳐서 공격한다. 언제나 40의 데미지를 준다.

name: Fire Spin
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. For the next 2–5 turns, the target cannot leave the field and is damaged for 1/16 its max HP at the end of each turn. The user continues to use other moves during this time. If the user leaves the field, this effect ends. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use. rapid spin cancels this effect.
effect_entry_ko: 세차게 소용돌이치는 불꽃 속에 4-5턴 동안 상대를 가두어 공격한다.

name: Thunder Shock
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to paralyze the target.
effect_entry_ko: 전기 자극을 상대에게 날려서 공격한다. 마비 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Thunderbolt
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to paralyze the target.
effect_entry_ko: 강한 전격을 상대에게 날려서 공격한다. 마비 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Thunder Wave
effect_entry: Paralyzes the target.
effect_entry_ko: 약한 전격을 날려서 상대를 마비 상태로 만든다.

name: Thunder
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to paralyze the target. During rain dance, this move has 100% accuracy. It also has a (100 - accuracy)% chance to break through the protection of protect and detect. During sunny day, this move has 50% accuracy.
effect_entry_ko: 강한 번개를 상대에게 떨어뜨려 공격한다. 마비 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Rock Throw
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 작은 바위를 들어올려 상대에게 내던져서 공격한다.

name: Earthquake
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target is in the first turn of dig, this move will hit with double power.
effect_entry_ko: 지진의 충격으로 자신의 주위에 있는 포켓몬을 공격한다.

name: Fissure
effect_entry: Inflicts damage equal to the target's max HP. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers. This move's accuracy is 30% plus 1% for each level the user is higher than the target. If the user is a lower level than the target, this move will fail. Because this move inflicts a specific and finite amount of damage, endure still prevents the target from fainting. The effects of lock on, mind reader, and no guard still apply, as long as the user is equal or higher level than the target. However, they will not give this move a chance to break through detect or protect.
effect_entry_ko: 땅이 갈라진 곳에 상대를 떨어뜨려 공격한다. 맞으면 일격에 기절한다.

name: Dig
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User digs underground for one turn, becoming immune to attack, and hits on the second turn. During the immune turn, earthquake, fissure, and magnitude still hit the user normally, and their power is doubled if appropriate. The user may be hit during its immune turn if under the effect of lock on, mind reader, or no guard. This move cannot be selected by sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 1턴째에 파고들어 2턴째에 상대를 공격한다. 동굴에서 탈출할 수도 있다.

name: Toxic
effect_entry: Badly poisons the target. Never misses when used by a poison-type Pokémon.
effect_entry_ko: 상대를 맹독의 상태로 만든다. 턴이 진행될수록 독의 데미지가 증가한다.

name: Confusion
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to confuse the target.
effect_entry_ko: 약한 염동력을 상대에게 보내어 공격한다. 상대를 혼란시킬 때가 있다.

name: Psychic
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to lower the target's Special Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 강한 염동력을 상대에게 보내어 공격한다. 상대의 특수방어를 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Hypnosis
effect_entry: Puts the target to sleep.
effect_entry_ko: 졸음을 유도하는 암시를 걸어서 상대를 잠듦 상태로 만든다.

name: Meditate
effect_entry: Raises the user's Attack by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 잠들어 있는 힘을 몸속에서 끌어내어 자신의 공격을 올린다.

name: Agility
effect_entry: Raises the user's Speed by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 힘을 빼고 몸을 가볍게 해서 고속으로 움직인다. 자신의 스피드를 크게 올린다.

name: Quick Attack
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 눈에 보이지 않는 굉장한 속도로 상대에게 돌진한다. 반드시 선제공격할 수 있다.

name: Rage
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Every time the user is hit after it uses this move but before its next action, its Attack raises by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 기술을 썼을 때 공격을 받으면 분노의 힘으로 공격이 올라간다.

name: Teleport
effect_entry: Does nothing. Wild battles end immediately.
effect_entry_ko: 야생 포켓몬과 배틀을 그만둔다. 마지막에 들어갔던 포켓몬센터가 있는 도시에도 갈 수 있다.

name: Night Shade
effect_entry: Inflicts damage equal to the user's level. Type immunity applies, but other type effects are ignored.
effect_entry_ko: 무시무시한 환상을 보게 해서 자신의 레벨과 똑같은 만큼의 데미지를 상대에게 준다.

name: Mimic
effect_entry: This move is replaced by the target's last successfully used move, and its PP changes to 5. If the target hasn't used a move since entering the field, if it tried to use a move this turn and failed, or if the user already knows the targeted move, this move will fail. This effect vanishes when the user leaves the field. If chatter, metronome, mimic, sketch, or struggle is selected, this move will fail. This move cannot be copied by mirror move, nor selected by assist or metronome, nor forced by encore.
effect_entry_ko: 상대가 마지막에 사용한 기술을 배틀을 하는 동안 자신의 기술로 만들 수 있다.

name: Screech
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Defense by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 그만 귀를 막아버리고 싶은 싫은 소리를 내어 상대의 방어를 크게 떨어뜨린다.

name: Double Team
effect_entry: Raises the user's evasion by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 재빠른 움직임으로 분신을 만들어 상대를 혼란시켜 회피율을 올린다.

name: Recover
effect_entry: Heals the user for half its max HP.
effect_entry_ko: 세포를 재생시켜 자신의 최대 HP의 절반만큼 HP를 회복한다.

name: Harden
effect_entry: Raises the user's Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 전신에 힘을 담아 몸을 단단하게 해서 자신의 방어를 올린다.

name: Minimize
effect_entry: Raises the user's evasion by two stages. stomp and steamroller have double power against Pokémon that have used this move since entering the field.
effect_entry_ko: 몸을 축소하여 작게 보임으로써 자신의 회피율을 크게 올린다.

name: Smokescreen
effect_entry: Lowers the target's accuracy by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 연기나 먹물을 내뿜어 상대의 명중률을 떨어뜨린다.

name: Confuse Ray
effect_entry: Confuses the target.
effect_entry_ko: 이상한 빛을 상대에게 비춰 당황하게 한다. 상대를 혼란시킨다.

name: Withdraw
effect_entry: Raises the user's Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 껍질에 숨어 몸을 보호하여 자신의 방어를 올린다.

name: Defense Curl
effect_entry: Raises user's Defense by one stage. After this move is used, the power of ice ball and rollout are doubled until the user leaves the field.
effect_entry_ko: 몸을 둥글게 웅크려서 자신의 방어를 올린다.

name: Barrier
effect_entry: Raises the user's Defense by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 튼튼한 장막을 만들어 자신의 방어를 크게 올린다.

name: Light Screen
effect_entry: Erects a barrier around the user's side of the field that reduces damage from special attacks by half for five turns. In double battles, the reduction is 1/3. Critical hits are not affected by the barrier. If the user is holding light clay, the barrier lasts for eight turns. brick break or defog used by an opponent will destroy the barrier.
effect_entry_ko: 5턴 동안 이상한 장막으로 상대로부터 받는 특수공격의 데미지를 약하게 한다.

name: Haze
effect_entry: Removes stat, accuracy, and evasion modifiers from every Pokémon on the field. This does not count as a stat reduction for the purposes of clear body or white smoke.
effect_entry_ko: 흑안개를 뿜어 배틀에 참가 중인 포켓몬 전원의 능력 변화를 원래대로 돌린다.

name: Reflect
effect_entry: Erects a barrier around the user's side of the field that reduces damage from physical attacks by half for five turns. In double battles, the reduction is 1/3. Critical hits are not affected by the barrier. If the user is holding light clay, the barrier lasts for eight turns. brick break or defog used by an opponent will destroy the barrier.
effect_entry_ko: 5턴 동안 이상한 장막으로 상대로부터 받는 물리공격의 데미지를 약하게 한다.

name: Focus Energy
effect_entry: User's critical hit rate is two levels higher until it leaves the field. If the user has already used focus energy since entering the field, this move will fail. This effect is passed on by baton pass.
effect_entry_ko: 깊게 숨을 들이마셔 기합을 넣는다. 자신의 공격이 급소에 맞기 쉬워진다.

name: Bide
effect_entry: User waits for two turns. On the second turn, the user inflicts twice the damage it accumulated on the last Pokémon to hit it. Damage inflicted is typeless. This move cannot be selected by sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 2턴 동안 공격을 견뎌 입은 데미지를 2배로 만들어 상대에게 돌려준다.

name: Metronome
effect_entry: Selects any move at random and uses it. Moves the user already knows are not eligible. Assist, meta, protection, and reflection moves are also not eligible; specifically, assist, chatter, copycat, counter, covet, destiny bond, detect, endure, feint, focus punch, follow me, helping hand, me first, metronome, mimic, mirror coat, mirror move, protect, quick guard, sketch, sleep talk, snatch, struggle, switcheroo, thief, trick, and wide guard will not be selected by this move. This move cannot be copied by mimic or mirror move, nor selected by assist, metronome, or sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 손가락을 흔들어 자신의 뇌를 자극해서 모든 기술 중 어느 하나를 날린다.

name: Mirror Move
effect_entry: Uses the last move targeted at the user by a Pokémon still on the field. A move counts as targeting the user even if it hit multiple Pokémon, as long as the user was one of them; however, moves targeting the field itself do not count. If the user has not been targeted by an appropriate move since entering the field, or if no Pokémon that targeted the user remains on the field, this move will fail. Moves that failed, missed, had no effect, or were blocked are still copied. Assist moves, time-delayed moves, “meta” moves that operate on other moves/Pokémon/abilities, and some other special moves cannot be copied and are ignored; if the last move to hit the user was such a move, the previous move will be used instead. The full list of ignored moves is: acid armor, acupressure, after you, agility, ally switch, amnesia, aqua ring, aromatherapy, aromatic mist, assist, autotomize, barrier, baton pass, belch, belly drum, bide, bulk up, calm mind, camouflage, celebrate, charge, coil, conversion, conversion 2, copycat, cosmic power, cotton guard, counter, crafty shield, curse, defend order, defense curl, destiny bond, detect, doom desire, double team, dragon dance, electric terrain, endure, final gambit, flower shield, focus energy, focus punch, follow me, future sight, geomancy, grassy terrain, gravity, growth, grudge, guard split, hail, happy hour, harden, haze, heal bell, heal order, heal pulse, healing wish, helping hand, hold hands, hone claws, howl, imprison, ingrain, ion deluge, iron defense, kings shield, light screen, lucky chant, lunar dance, magic coat, magnet rise, magnetic flux, mat block, me first, meditate, metronome, milk drink, mimic, minimize, mirror coat, mirror move, mist, misty terrain, moonlight, morning sun, mud sport, nasty plot, nature power, perish song, power split, power trick, protect, psych up, quick guard, quiver dance, rage powder, rain dance, recover, recycle, reflect, reflect type, refresh, rest, rock polish, role play, roost, rototiller, safeguard, sandstorm, shadow blast, shadow bolt, shadow half, shadow rush, shadow shed, shadow sky, shadow storm, shadow wave, sharpen, shell smash, shift gear, sketch, slack off, sleep talk, snatch, soft boiled, spikes, spiky shield, spit up, splash, stealth rock, sticky web, stockpile, struggle, substitute, sunny day, swallow, swords dance, synthesis, tail glow, tailwind, teleport, toxic spikes, transform, water sport, wide guard, wish, withdraw and work up. This move cannot be selected by assist, metronome, or sleep talk, nor forced by encore.
effect_entry_ko: 상대가 사용한 기술을 흉내 내어 자신도 똑같은 기술을 쓴다.

name: Self-Destruct
effect_entry: User faints, even if the attack fails or misses. Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 폭발을 일으켜서 자신의 주위에 있는 포켓몬을 공격한다. 쓰고 나서 기절하게 된다.

name: Egg Bomb
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 큰 알을 온 힘을 다해 상대에게 내던져서 공격한다.

name: Lick
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to paralyze the target.
effect_entry_ko: 긴 혀로 상대를 핥아서 공격한다. 마비 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Smog
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 40% chance to poison the target.
effect_entry_ko: 더러운 가스를 상대에게 내뿜어 공격한다. 독 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Sludge
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to poison the target.
effect_entry_ko: 더러운 오물을 상대에게 내던져서 공격한다. 독 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Bone Club
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 손에 들고 있는 뼈로 상대를 세게 때려서 공격한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: Fire Blast
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to burn the target.
effect_entry_ko: 큰 대자의 불꽃으로 상대를 불태운다. 화상 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Waterfall
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 20% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 굉장한 기세로 상대에게 돌진한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다. 폭포도 거슬러 올라갈 수 있다.

name: Clamp
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. For the next 2–5 turns, the target cannot leave the field and is damaged for 1/16 its max HP at the end of each turn. The user continues to use other moves during this time. If the user leaves the field, this effect ends. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use. rapid spin cancels this effect.
effect_entry_ko: 매우 튼튼하고 두꺼운 껍질에 4-5턴 동안 상대를 끼워서 공격한다.

name: Swift
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers.
effect_entry_ko: 별 모양의 빛을 발사해서 상대를 공격한다. 공격은 반드시 명중한다.

name: Skull Bash
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Raises the user's Defense by one stage. User then charges for one turn before attacking. This move cannot be selected by sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 1턴째에 머리를 움츠려 방어를 올린다. 2턴째에 상대를 공격한다.

name: Spike Cannon
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits 2–5 times in one turn. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use.
effect_entry_ko: 날카로운 침을 상대에게 발사해서 공격한다. 2-5회 동안 연속으로 쓴다.

name: Constrict
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to lower the target's Speed by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 촉수나 덩굴 등을 휘감아서 공격한다. 상대의 스피드를 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Amnesia
effect_entry: Raises the user's Special Defense by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 머리를 비워서 순간적으로 무언가를 잊어버림으로써 자신의 특수방어를 크게 올린다.

name: Kinesis
effect_entry: Lowers the target's accuracy by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 숟가락을 휘어서 주의를 끌어 상대의 명중률을 낮춘다.

name: Soft-Boiled
effect_entry: Heals the user for half its max HP.
effect_entry_ko: 자신의 최대 HP 절반을 회복한다. 동료에게 HP를 나누어 줄 수도 있다.

name: High Jump Kick
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If this move misses, is blocked by protect or detect, or has no effect, the user takes damage equal to half of its max HP rounded down. This move cannot be used while gravity is in effect.
effect_entry_ko: 점프해서 무릎차기로 상대를 공격한다. 빗나가면 자신이 데미지를 입는다.

name: Glare
effect_entry: Paralyzes the target.
effect_entry_ko: 배의 무늬로 겁을 주어 상대를 마비 상태로 만든다.

name: Dream Eater
effect_entry: Fails if not used on a sleeping Pokémon. Inflicts regular damage. Drains half the damage inflicted to heal the user.
effect_entry_ko: 잠자고 있는 상대의 꿈을 먹어 공격한다. 데미지의 절반을 HP로 회복한다.

name: Poison Gas
effect_entry: Poisons the target.
effect_entry_ko: 독가스를 상대의 얼굴에 내뿜어 독 상태로 만든다.

name: Barrage
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits 2–5 times in one turn. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use.
effect_entry_ko: 둥근 것을 상대에게 내던져서 공격한다. 2-5회 동안 연속으로 쓴다.

name: Leech Life
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Drains half the damage inflicted to heal the user.
effect_entry_ko: 피를 빨아서 상대를 공격한다. 준 데미지의 절반을 HP로 회복한다.

name: Lovely Kiss
effect_entry: Puts the target to sleep.
effect_entry_ko: 무서운 얼굴로 키스한다. 상대를 잠듦 상태로 만든다.

name: Sky Attack
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User charges for one turn before attacking. Critical hit chance is one level higher than normal. Has a 30% chance to make the target flinch. This move cannot be selected by sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 2턴째에 상대를 공격한다. 가끔 풀죽게 만든다. 급소에도 맞기 쉽다.

name: Transform
effect_entry: User copies the target's species, weight, type, ability, calculated stats (except HP), and moves. Copied moves will all have 5 PP remaining. IVs are copied for the purposes of hidden power, but stats are not recalculated. choice band, choice scarf, and choice specs stay in effect, and the user must select a new move. This move cannot be copied by mirror move, nor forced by encore.
effect_entry_ko: 상대 포켓몬으로 변신하여 상대와 완전히 똑같은 기술을 사용할 수 있다.

name: Bubble
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to lower the target's Speed by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 매우 많은 거품을 상대에게 내뿜어 공격한다. 상대의 스피드를 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Dizzy Punch
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 20% chance to confuse the target.
effect_entry_ko: 리드미컬한 펀치를 날려 상대를 공격한다. 혼란시킬 때가 있다.

name: Spore
effect_entry: Puts the target to sleep.
effect_entry_ko: 최면 효과가 있는 포자를 훌훌 흩뿌려서 상대를 잠듦 상태로 만든다.

name: Flash
effect_entry: Lowers the target's accuracy by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 눈이 부신 빛으로 상대의 명중률을 떨어뜨린다.

name: Psywave
effect_entry: Inflicts typeless damage between 50% and 150% of the user's level, selected at random in increments of 10%.
effect_entry_ko: 이상한 염력파를 상대에게 발사하여 공격한다. 사용할 때마다 데미지가 바뀐다.

name: Splash
effect_entry: Does nothing. This move cannot be used while gravity is in effect.
effect_entry_ko: 공격도 하지 않고 팔딱팔딱 튈 뿐 아무 일도 일어나지 않는다...

name: Acid Armor
effect_entry: Raises the user's Defense by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 세포의 변화로 액체가 되어 자신의 방어를 크게 올린다.

name: Crabhammer
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move.
effect_entry_ko: 큰 집게를 상대에게 내리쳐서 공격한다. 급소에 맞기 쉽다.

name: Explosion
effect_entry: User faints, even if the attack fails or misses. Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 큰 폭발로 자신의 주위에 있는 포켓몬을 공격한다. 쓰고 나서는 기절한다.

name: Fury Swipes
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits 2–5 times in one turn. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use.
effect_entry_ko: 손톱이나 낫 등으로 상대를 할퀴어서 공격한다. 2-5회 동안 연속으로 쓴다.

name: Bonemerang
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits twice in one turn.
effect_entry_ko: 손에 들고 있는 뼈를 상대에게 날려서 날아갈 때와 돌아올 때 2회 연속 데미지를 준다.

name: Rest
effect_entry: User falls to sleep and immediately regains all its HP. If the user has another major status effect, sleep will replace it. The user will always wake up after two turns, or one turn with early bird. This move fails if the Pokémon cannot fall asleep due to uproar, insomnia, or vital spirit. It also fails if the Pokémon is at full health or is already asleep.
effect_entry_ko: 2턴 동안 계속 잠잔다. 자신의 HP와 상태 이상을 모두 회복한다.

name: Rock Slide
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 큰 바위를 세차게 부딪쳐서 공격한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: Hyper Fang
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 날카로운 앞니로 강하게 물어서 공격한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: Sharpen
effect_entry: Raises the user's Attack by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 몸의 각을 늘려서 더욱 각지게 하여 자신의 공격을 올린다.

name: Conversion
effect_entry: User's type changes to the type of one of its moves, selected at random. hidden power and weather ball are treated as normal. Only moves with a different type are eligible, and curse is never eligible. If the user has no suitable moves, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 자신의 타입을 배운 기술 중 가장 위에 있는 기술과 같은 타입으로 바꾼다.

name: Tri Attack
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 20% chance to burn, freeze, or paralyze the target. One of these effects is selected at random; they each have independent chances to occur.
effect_entry_ko: 3개의 광선으로 공격한다. 마비, 화상 또는 얼음 상태 중 어느 하나로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Super Fang
effect_entry: Inflicts typeless damage equal to half the target's remaining HP.
effect_entry_ko: 날카로운 앞니로 강하게 물어서 공격한다. 상대의 HP는 절반이 된다.

name: Slash
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move.
effect_entry_ko: 발톱이나 낫 등으로 상대를 베어 갈라서 공격한다. 급소에 맞기 쉽다.

name: Substitute
effect_entry: Transfers 1/4 the user's max HP into a doll that absorbs damage and causes most negative move effects to fail. If the user leaves the field, the doll will vanish. If the user cannot pay the HP cost, this move will fail. The doll takes damage as normal, using the user's stats and types, and will break when its HP reaches zero. Self-inflicted damage from confusion or recoil is not absorbed. Healing effects from opponents ignore the doll and heal the user as normal. Moves that work based on the user's HP still do so; the doll's HP does not influence any move. The doll will block major status effects, confusion, and flinching. The effects of smelling salts and wake up slap do not trigger against a doll, even if the Pokémon behind the doll has the appropriate major status effect. Multi-turn trapping moves like wrap will hit the doll for their regular damage, but the multi-turn trapping and damage effects will not activate. Moves blocked or damage absorbed by the doll do not count as hitting the user or inflicting damage for any effects that respond to such, e.g., avalanche, counter, or a rowap berry. magic coat still works as normal, even against moves the doll would block. Opposing Pokémon that damage the doll with a leech move like absorb are healed as normal. It will also block acupressure, block, the curse effect of curse, dream eater, embargo, flatter, gastro acid, grudge, heal block, leech seed, lock on, mean look, mimic, mind reader, nightmare, pain split, psycho shift, spider web, sketch, swagger, switcheroo, trick, worry seed, and yawn. A Pokémon affected by yawn before summoning the doll will still fall to sleep. The doll blocks intimidate, but all other abilities act as though the doll did not exist. If the user has an ability that absorbs moves of a certain type for HP (such as volt absorb absorbing thunder wave), such moves will not be blocked. life orb and berries that cause confusion still work as normal, but their respective HP loss and confusion are absorbed/blocked by the doll. The user is still vulnerable to damage inflicted when entering or leaving the field, such as by pursuit or spikes; however, the doll will block the poison effect of toxic spikes. The doll is passed on by baton pass. It keeps its existing HP, but uses the replacement Pokémon's stats and types for damage calculation. All other effects work as normal.
effect_entry_ko: 자신의 HP를 조금 깎아서 분신을 만든다. 분신은 자신의 대타가 된다.

name: Struggle
effect_entry: Inflicts typeless regular damage. User takes 1/4 its max HP in recoil. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers. This move is used automatically when a Pokémon cannot use any other move legally, e.g., due to having no PP remaining or being under the effect of both encore and torment at the same time. This move's recoil is not treated as recoil for the purposes of anything that affects recoil, such as the ability rock head. It also is not prevented by magic guard. This move cannot be copied by mimic, mirror move, or sketch, nor selected by assist or metronome, nor forced by encore.
effect_entry_ko: 자신의 PP가 떨어지면 발버둥 쳐 상대를 공격한다. 자신도 조금 데미지를 입는다.

name: Sketch
effect_entry: Permanently replaces itself with the target's last used move. If that move is chatter or struggle, this move will fail. This move cannot be copied by mimic or mirror move, nor selected by assist or metronome, nor forced by encore.
effect_entry_ko: 상대가 쓴 기술을 자신의 것으로 만든다. 한 번 사용하면 스케치는 사라진다.

name: Triple Kick
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits three times in the same turn. The second hit has double power, and the third hit has triple power. Each hit has a separate accuracy check, and this move stops if a hit misses. skill link does not apply.
effect_entry_ko: 3회 연속으로 킥을 날려 공격한다. 기술이 맞을 때마다 위력이 올라간다.

name: Thief
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target is holding an item and the user is not, the user will permanently take the item. Damage is still inflicted if an item cannot be taken. Pokémon with sticky hold or multitype are immune to the item theft effect. The target cannot recover its item with recycle. This move cannot be selected by assist or metronome.
effect_entry_ko: 공격과 동시에 도구를 훔친다. 자신이 도구를 지니고 있을 경우에는 훔칠 수 없다.

name: Spider Web
effect_entry: The target cannot switch out normally. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers. This effect ends when the user leaves the field. The target may still escape by using baton pass, u turn, or a shed shell. Both the user and the target pass on this effect with baton pass.
effect_entry_ko: 끈적끈적하고 가는 실을 칭칭 휘감아 상대를 배틀에서 도망칠 수 없게 한다.

name: Mind Reader
effect_entry: If the user targets the same target again before the end of the next turn, the move it uses is guaranteed to hit. This move itself also ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers. One-hit KO moves are also guaranteed to hit, as long as the user is equal or higher level than the target. This effect also allows the user to hit Pokémon that are off the field due to moves such as dig or fly. If the target uses detect or protect while under the effect of this move, the user is not guaranteed to hit, but has a (100 - accuracy)% chance to break through the protection. This effect is passed on by baton pass.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 움직임을 마음으로 읽고 다음 공격이 반드시 상대에게 명중되게 한다.

name: Nightmare
effect_entry: Only works on sleeping Pokémon. Gives the target a nightmare, damaging it for 1/4 its max HP every turn. If the target wakes up or leaves the field, this effect ends.
effect_entry_ko: 잠듦 상태의 상대에게 악몽을 꾸게 하여 매 턴 조금씩 HP를 떨어뜨려 간다.

name: Flame Wheel
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to burn the target. Frozen Pokémon may use this move, in which case they will thaw.
effect_entry_ko: 불꽃을 둘러 상대에게 돌진하여 공격한다. 화상 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Snore
effect_entry: Only usable if the user is sleeping. Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 자신이 잠들어있을 때 소음을 내어 공격한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: Curse
effect_entry: If the user is a ghost: user pays half its max HP to place a curse on the target, damaging it for 1/4 its max HP every turn. Otherwise: Lowers the user's Speed by one stage, and raises its Attack and Defense by one stage each. The curse effect is passed on by baton pass. This move cannot be copied by mirror move.
effect_entry_ko: 기술을 쓰는 포켓몬이 고스트타입일 때와 그 이외의 타입일 때는 효과가 다르다.

name: Flail
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power varies inversely with the user's proportional remaining HP. 64 * current HP / max HP | Power -----------------------: | ----: 0– 1          | 200 2– 5          | 150 6–12          | 100 13–21          |  80 22–42          |  40 43–64          |  20
effect_entry_ko: 바둥바둥 난동 부려서 공격한다. 자신의 HP가 적을수록 기술의 위력이 올라간다.

name: Conversion 2
effect_entry: Changes the user's type to a type either resistant or immune to the last damaging move that hit it. The new type is selected at random and cannot be a type the user already is. If there is no eligible new type, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 상대가 마지막으로 쓴 기술에 저항할 수 있도록 자신의 타입을 변화시킨다.

name: Aeroblast
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move.
effect_entry_ko: 공기의 소용돌이를 발사하여 공격한다. 급소에 맞기 쉽다.

name: Cotton Spore
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Speed by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 솜처럼 폭신폭신한 포자를 착 달라붙게 해서 상대의 스피드를 크게 떨어뜨린다.

name: Reversal
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power varies inversely with the user's proportional remaining HP. 64 * current HP / max HP | Power -----------------------: | ----: 0– 1          | 200 2– 5          | 150 6–12          | 100 13–21          |  80 22–42          |  40 43–64          |  20
effect_entry_ko: 힘을 쥐어짜서 공격한다. 자신의 HP가 적을수록 기술의 위력이 올라간다.

name: Spite
effect_entry: Lowers the PP of the target's last used move by 4. If the target hasn't used a move since entering the field, if it tried to use a move this turn and failed, or if its last used move has 0 PP remaining, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 상대가 마지막으로 사용한 기술에 원한을 품어 그 기술의 PP를 4만큼 줄인다.

name: Powder Snow
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to freeze the target.
effect_entry_ko: 차가운 가랑눈을 상대에게 내뿜어 공격한다. 얼음 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Protect
effect_entry: No moves will hit the user for the remainder of this turn. If the user is last to act this turn, this move will fail. If the user successfully used detect, endure, protect, quick guard, or wide guard on the last turn, this move has a 50% chance to fail. lock on, mind reader, and no guard provide a (100 – accuracy)% chance for moves to break through this move. This does not apply to one-hit KO moves (fissure, guillotine, horn drill, and sheer cold); those are always blocked by this move. thunder during rain dance and blizzard during hail have a 30% chance to break through this move. The following effects are not prevented by this move: * acupressure from an ally * curse's curse effect * Delayed damage from doom desire and future sight; however, these moves will be prevented if they are used this turn * feint, which will also end this move's protection after it hits * imprison * perish song * shadow force * Moves that merely copy the user, such as transform or psych up This move cannot be selected by assist or metronome.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 공격을 전혀 받지 않는다. 연속으로 쓰면 실패하기 쉽다.

name: Mach Punch
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 눈에 보이지 않는 굉장한 속도로 펀치를 날린다. 반드시 선제공격을 할 수 있다.

name: Scary Face
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Speed by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 무서운 얼굴로 노려보고 겁주어 상대의 스피드를 크게 떨어뜨린다.

name: Feint Attack
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers.
effect_entry_ko: 슬금슬금 상대에게 다가가 방심한 틈을 타서 세게 때린다. 공격은 반드시 명중한다.

name: Sweet Kiss
effect_entry: Confuses the target.
effect_entry_ko: 천사처럼 귀엽게 키스하여 상대를 혼란시킨다.

name: Belly Drum
effect_entry: User pays half its max HP to raise its Attack to +6 stages. If the user cannot pay the HP cost, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 자신의 HP를 최대 HP의 절반만큼 감소시켜 자신의 공격을 최대로 올린다.

name: Sludge Bomb
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to poison the target.
effect_entry_ko: 더러운 오물을 상대에게 내던져서 공격한다. 독 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Mud-Slap
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 100% chance to lower the target's accuracy by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 얼굴 등에 진흙을 내던져서 공격한다. 명중률을 떨어뜨린다.

name: Octazooka
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 50% chance to lower the target's accuracy by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 얼굴 등에 먹물을 내뿜어 공격한다. 명중률을 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Spikes
effect_entry: Scatters spikes around the opposing field, which damage opposing Pokémon that enter the field for 1/8 of their max HP. Pokémon immune to ground moves are immune to this damage, except during gravity. Up to three layers of spikes may be laid down, adding 1/16 to the damage done: two layers of spikes damage for 3/16 max HP, and three layers damage for 1/4 max HP. wonder guard does not block damage from this effect. rapid spin removes this effect from its user's side of the field. defog removes this effect from its target's side of the field.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 발밑에 압정을 뿌린다. 교체된 상대 포켓몬에게 데미지를 준다.

name: Zap Cannon
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 100% chance to paralyze the target.
effect_entry_ko: 대포처럼 전기를 발사해서 공격한다. 상대를 마비 상태로 만든다.

name: Foresight
effect_entry: Resets the target's evasion to normal and prevents any further boosting until the target leaves the field. A ghost under this effect takes normal damage from normal and fighting moves. This move itself ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers.
effect_entry_ko: 고스트타입에 효과가 없는 기술이나 회피율이 높은 상대라 할지라도 공격이 맞게 된다.

name: Destiny Bond
effect_entry: If the user faints before its next move, the Pokémon that fainted it will automatically faint. End-of-turn damage is ignored. This move cannot be selected by assist or metronome.
effect_entry_ko: 기술을 쓴 뒤 공격을 받아 기절했을 때 길동무의 대상도 기절하게 한다.

name: Perish Song
effect_entry: Every Pokémon is given a counter that starts at 3 and decreases by 1 at the end of every turn, including this one. When a Pokémon's counter reaches zero, that Pokémon faints. A Pokémon that leaves the field will lose its counter; its replacement does not inherit the effect, and other Pokémon's counters remain. This effect is passed on by baton pass. This move cannot be copied by mirror move.
effect_entry_ko: 노래를 들은 포켓몬은 3턴이 지나면 기절한다. 교체되면 효과가 없어진다.

name: Icy Wind
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 100% chance to lower the target's Speed by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 차가운 냉기를 상대에게 내뿜어 공격한다. 상대의 스피드를 떨어뜨린다.

name: Detect
effect_entry: No moves will hit the user for the remainder of this turn. If the user is last to act this turn, this move will fail. If the user successfully used detect, endure, protect, quick guard, or wide guard on the last turn, this move has a 50% chance to fail. lock on, mind reader, and no guard provide a (100 – accuracy)% chance for moves to break through this move. This does not apply to one-hit KO moves (fissure, guillotine, horn drill, and sheer cold); those are always blocked by this move. thunder during rain dance and blizzard during hail have a 30% chance to break through this move. The following effects are not prevented by this move: * acupressure from an ally * curse's curse effect * Delayed damage from doom desire and future sight; however, these moves will be prevented if they are used this turn * feint, which will also end this move's protection after it hits * imprison * perish song * shadow force * Moves that merely copy the user, such as transform or psych up This move cannot be selected by assist or metronome.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 공격을 전혀 받지 않는다. 연속으로 쓰면 실패하기 쉽다.

name: Bone Rush
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits 2–5 times in one turn. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use.
effect_entry_ko: 단단한 뼈로 상대를 세게 때려서 공격한다. 2-5회 동안 연속으로 쓴다.

name: Lock-On
effect_entry: If the user targets the same target again before the end of the next turn, the move it uses is guaranteed to hit. This move itself also ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers. One-hit KO moves are also guaranteed to hit, as long as the user is equal or higher level than the target. This effect also allows the user to hit Pokémon that are off the field due to moves such as dig or fly. If the target uses detect or protect while under the effect of this move, the user is not guaranteed to hit, but has a (100 - accuracy)% chance to break through the protection. This effect is passed on by baton pass.
effect_entry_ko: 조준을 잘 맞춰 다음 공격이 반드시 상대에게 명중하도록 한다.

name: Outrage
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User is forced to attack with this move for 2–3 turns,selected at random. After the last hit, the user becomes confused. safeguard does not protect against the confusion from this move.
effect_entry_ko: 2-3턴 동안 마구 난동 부려서 공격한다. 난동 부린 뒤에는 혼란에 빠진다.

name: Sandstorm
effect_entry: Changes the weather to a sandstorm for five turns. Pokémon that are not ground, rock, or steel take 1/16 their max HP at the end of every turn. Every rock Pokémon's original Special Defense is raised by 50% for the duration of this effect. solar beam's power is halved. moonlight, morning sun, and synthesis only heal 1/4 the user's max HP.
effect_entry_ko: 5턴 동안 모래바람으로 바위, 땅, 강철타입 이외의 포켓몬에게 데미지를 준다.

name: Giga Drain
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Drains half the damage inflicted to heal the user.
effect_entry_ko: 양분을 흡수하여 공격한다. 입힌 데미지의 절반에 해당하는 HP를 회복할 수 있다.

name: Endure
effect_entry: The user's HP cannot be lowered below 1 by any means for the remainder of this turn. If the user successfully used detect, endure, protect, quick guard, or wide guard on the last turn, this move has a 50% chance to fail. This move cannot be selected by assist or metronome.
effect_entry_ko: 공격을 받아도 HP를 반드시 1만큼은 남긴다. 연속으로 쓰면 실패하기 쉽다.

name: Charm
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Attack by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 귀엽게 바라보고 방심을 유도하여 상대의 공격을 크게 떨어뜨린다.

name: Rollout
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User is forced to use this move for five turns. Power doubles every time this move is used in succession to a maximum of 16x, and resets to normal after the lock-in ends. If this move misses or becomes unusable, the lock-in ends. If the user has used defense curl since entering the field, this move has double power.
effect_entry_ko: 5턴 동안 구르기를 반복하여 공격한다. 기술이 맞을 때마다 위력이 올라간다.

name: False Swipe
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Will not reduce the target's HP below 1.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 HP가 반드시 1만큼 남도록 조절하여 공격한다.

name: Swagger
effect_entry: Raises the target's Attack by two stages, then confuses it. If the target's Attack cannot be raised by two stages, the confusion is not applied.
effect_entry_ko: 상대를 화내게 해서 혼란시킨다. 분노로 상대의 공격은 크게 올라가 버린다.

name: Milk Drink
effect_entry: Heals the user for half its max HP.
effect_entry_ko: 자신의 최대 HP 절반을 회복한다. 동료에게 HP를 나누어 줄 수도 있다.

name: Spark
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to paralyze the target.
effect_entry_ko: 전기를 둘러 상대에게 돌진하여 공격한다. 마비 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Fury Cutter
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power doubles after every time this move is used, whether consecutively or not, maxing out at 16x. If this move misses or the user leaves the field, power resets.
effect_entry_ko: 낫이나 발톱 등으로 상대를 베어 공격한다. 연속으로 맞히면 위력이 올라간다.

name: Steel Wing
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to raise the user's Defense one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 단단한 날개를 상대에게 부딪쳐서 공격한다. 자신의 방어가 올라갈 때가 있다.

name: Mean Look
effect_entry: The target cannot switch out normally. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers. This effect ends when the user leaves the field. The target may still escape by using baton pass, u turn, or a shed shell. Both the user and the target pass on this effect with baton pass.
effect_entry_ko: 빨려 들어갈 것 같은 까만 눈빛으로 가만히 응시하여 상대를 배틀에서 도망갈 수 없게 한다.

name: Attract
effect_entry: Causes the target to fall in love with the user, giving it a 50% chance to do nothing each turn. If the user and target are the same gender, or either is genderless, this move will fail. If either Pokémon leaves the field, this effect ends.
effect_entry_ko: 수컷은 암컷을 암컷은 수컷을 유혹하여 헤롱헤롱하게 만든다. 상대가 기술을 쓰기 어려워진다.

name: Sleep Talk
effect_entry: Only usable if the user is sleeping. Randomly selects and uses one of the user's other three moves. Use of the selected move requires and costs 0 PP. This move will not select assist, bide, bounce, chatter, copycat, dig, dive, fly, focus punch, me first, metronome, mirror move, shadow force, skull bash, sky attack, sky drop, sleep talk, solar beam, razor wind, or uproar. If the selected move requires a recharge turn—i.e., one of blast burn, frenzy plant, giga impact, hydro cannon, hyper beam, roar of time, or rock wrecker—and the user is still sleeping next turn, then it's forced to use this move again and pay another PP for the recharge turn. This move cannot be copied by mirror move, nor selected by assist, metronome, or sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 자신이 배운 기술 중 하나를 무작위로 날린다. 자신이 잠들어 있을 때만 쓸 수 있다.

name: Heal Bell
effect_entry: Removes major status effects and confusion from every Pokémon in the user's party.
effect_entry_ko: 기분 좋은 방울소리를 들려주어 같은 편 전원의 상태 이상을 회복한다.

name: Return
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power increases with happiness, given by `happiness * 2 / 5`, to a maximum of 102. Power bottoms out at 1.
effect_entry_ko: 트레이너를 위해 전력으로 상대를 공격한다. 친밀할수록 위력이 올라간다.

name: Present
effect_entry: Randomly uses one of the following effects. Effect                       | Chance -------------------------------------------------- | -----: Inflicts regular damage with 40 power |  40% Inflicts regular damage with 80 power |  30% Inflicts regular damage with 120 power |  10% Heals the target for 1/4 its max HP  |  20% On average, this move inflicts regular damage with 52 power and heals the target for 1/20 its max HP.
effect_entry_ko: 덫을 설치한 상자를 상대에게 건네어 공격한다. HP가 회복돼버릴 때도 있다.

name: Frustration
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power increases inversely with happiness, given by `(255 - happiness) * 2 / 5`, to a maximum of 102. Power bottoms out at 1.
effect_entry_ko: 불만을 풀기 위해 전력으로 상대를 공격한다. 친밀하지 않을수록 위력이 올라간다.

name: Safeguard
effect_entry: Protects Pokémon on the user's side of the field from major status effects and confusion for five turns. Does not cancel existing ailments. This effect remains even if the user leaves the field. If yawn is used while this move is in effect, it will immediately fail. defog used by an opponent will end this effect. This effect does not prevent the confusion caused by outrage, petal dance, or thrash.
effect_entry_ko: 5턴 동안 이상한 힘으로 보호받아 상태 이상이 되지 않는다.

name: Pain Split
effect_entry: Changes the user's and target's remaining HP to the average of their current remaining HP. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers. This effect does not count as inflicting damage for other moves and effects that respond to damage taken. This effect fails against a substitute.
effect_entry_ko: 자신의 HP와 상대의 HP를 합친 것을 자신과 상대가 사이좋게 나눈다.

name: Sacred Fire
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 50% chance to burn the target. Frozen Pokémon may use this move, in which case they will thaw.
effect_entry_ko: 신비한 불꽃으로 상대를 태워서 공격한다. 화상 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Magnitude
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power is selected at random between 10 and 150, with an average of 71: Magnitude | Power | Chance --------: | ----: | -----:     4 |  10 |   5%     5 |  30 |  10%     6 |  50 |  20%     7 |  70 |  30%     8 |  90 |  20%     9 |  110 |  10%    10 |  150 |   5% This move has double power against Pokémon currently underground due to dig.
effect_entry_ko: 땅을 흔들어서 자신의 주위에 있는 포켓몬을 공격한다. 기술의 위력이 여러모로 바뀐다.

name: Dynamic Punch
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 100% chance to confuse the target.
effect_entry_ko: 혼신의 힘으로 펀치를 날려서 공격한다. 상대를 반드시 혼란시킨다.

name: Megahorn
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 단단하고 훌륭한 뿔로 마음껏 상대를 꿰찔러서 공격한다.

name: Dragon Breath
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to paralyze the target.
effect_entry_ko: 굉장한 숨결을 상대에게 내뿜어 공격한다. 마비 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Baton Pass
effect_entry: User switches out, and the trainer selects a replacement Pokémon from the party. Stat changes, confusion, and persistent move effects are passed along to the replacement Pokémon. The following move effects are passed: * aqua ring * both the user's and target's effect of block, mean look, and spider web * the curse effect of curse * embargo * focus energy or an activated lansat berry * gastro acid * ingrain * being sapped by leech seed * being targeted by lock on or mind reader * magnet rise * perish song's counter * power trick * substitute; the doll's HP is unchanged The replacement Pokémon does not trigger effects that respond to Pokémon switching in.
effect_entry_ko: 교대 포켓몬과 바뀐다. 능력 변화는 바뀐 포켓몬이 그대로 이어받는다.

name: Encore
effect_entry: The next 4–8 times (selected at random) the target attempts to move, it is forced to repeat its last used move. If the selected move allows the trainer to select a target, an opponent will be selected at random each turn. If the target is prevented from using the selected move by some other effect, struggle will be used instead. This effect ends if the selected move runs out of PP. If the target hasn't used a move since entering the field, if it tried to use a move this turn and failed, if it does not know the selected move, or if the selected move has 0 PP remaining, this move will fail. If the target's last used move was encore, mimic, mirror move, sketch, struggle, or transform, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 상대가 마지막으로 사용한 기술을 3턴 동안 계속 쓰게 한다.

name: Pursuit
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target attempts to switch out this turn before the user acts, this move hits the target before it leaves and has double power. This effect can still hit a Pokémon that switches out when it has a substitute up or when an ally has used follow me.
effect_entry_ko: 상대 포켓몬이 교체될 때 기술을 쓰면 2배의 위력으로 공격할 수 있다.

name: Rapid Spin
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Removes leech seed from the user, frees the user from bind, clamp, fire spin, magma storm, sand tomb, whirlpool, and wrap, and clears spikes, stealth rock, and toxic spikes from the user's side of the field. If this move misses or has no effect, its effect doesn't activate.
effect_entry_ko: 회전해서 상대를 공격한다. 조이기, 김밥말이, 씨뿌리기, 압정뿌리기 등도 날려버린다.

name: Sweet Scent
effect_entry: Lowers the target's evasion by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 향기로 상대의 회피율을 크게 떨어뜨린다. 풀밭 등에서 쓰면 포켓몬이 다가온다.

name: Iron Tail
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to lower the target's Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 단단한 꼬리로 상대를 힘껏 쳐서 공격한다. 상대의 방어를 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Metal Claw
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to raise the user's Attack one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 강철의 발톱으로 상대를 베어 갈라 공격한다. 자신의 공격이 올라갈 때도 있다.

name: Vital Throw
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers.
effect_entry_ko: 상대보다 나중에 공격한다. 그 대신 자신의 공격은 반드시 명중한다.

name: Morning Sun
effect_entry: Heals the user for half its max HP. During sunny day, the healing is increased to 2/3 max HP. During hail, rain dance, or sandstorm, the healing is decreased to 1/4 max HP.
effect_entry_ko: 자신의 HP를 회복한다. 날씨에 따라 회복량이 변한다.

name: Synthesis
effect_entry: Heals the user for half its max HP. During sunny day, the healing is increased to 2/3 max HP. During hail, rain dance, or sandstorm, the healing is decreased to 1/4 max HP.
effect_entry_ko: 자신의 HP를 회복한다. 날씨에 따라 회복량이 변한다.

name: Moonlight
effect_entry: Heals the user for half its max HP. During sunny day, the healing is increased to 2/3 max HP. During hail, rain dance, or sandstorm, the healing is decreased to 1/4 max HP.
effect_entry_ko: 자신의 HP를 회복한다. 날씨에 따라 회복량이 변한다.

name: Hidden Power
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power and type are determined by the user's IVs. Power is given by `x * 40 / 63 + 30`. `x` is obtained by arranging bit 1 from the IV for each of Special Defense, Special Attack, Speed, Defense, Attack, and HP in that order. (Bit 1 is 1 if the IV is of the form `4n + 2` or `4n + 3`. `x` is then 64 * Special Defense IV bit 1, plus 32 * Special Attack IV bit 1, etc.) Power is always between 30 and 70, inclusive. Average power is 49.5. Type is given by `y * 15 / 63`, where `y` is similar to `x` above, except constructed from bit 0. (Bit 0 is 1 if the IV is odd.) The result is looked up in the following table. Value | Type ----: | --------   0 | fighting   1 | flying   2 | poison   3 | ground   4 | rock   5 | bug   6 | ghost   7 | steel   8 | fire   9 | water  10 | grass  11 | electric  12 | psychic  13 | ice  14 | dragon  15 | dark This move thus cannot be normal. Most other types have an equal 1/16 chance to be selected, given random IVs. However, due to the flooring used here, bug, fighting, and grass appear 5/64 of the time, and dark only 1/64 of the time.
effect_entry_ko: 기술을 쓴 포켓몬에 따라 기술의 타입이 바뀐다.

name: Cross Chop
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move.
effect_entry_ko: 양손으로 당수를 상대에게 힘껏 쳐서 공격한다. 급소에 맞기 쉽다.

name: Twister
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 20% chance to make each target flinch. If the target is under the effect of bounce, fly, or sky drop, this move will hit with double power.
effect_entry_ko: 회오리를 일으켜 상대를 끌어들여 공격한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: Rain Dance
effect_entry: Changes the weather to rain for five turns, during which water moves inflict 50% extra damage, and fire moves inflict half damage. If the user is holding damp rock, this effect lasts for eight turns. thunder has 100% accuracy. If the target has used detect or protect, thunder has a (100 - accuracy)% chance to break through the protection. solar beam has half power. moonlight, morning sun, and synthesis heal only 1/4 of the user's max HP. Pokémon with swift swim have doubled original Speed. Pokémon with forecast become water. Pokémon with dry skin heal 1/8 max HP, Pokémon with hydration are cured of major status effects, and Pokémon with rain dish heal 1/16 max HP at the end of each turn.
effect_entry_ko: 5턴 동안 비를 내리게 하여 물타입 기술의 위력을 올린다.

name: Sunny Day
effect_entry: Changes the weather to sunshine for five turns, during which fire moves inflict 50% extra damage, and water moves inflict half damage. If the user is holding heat rock, this effect lasts for eight turns. Pokémon cannot become frozen. thunder has 50% accuracy. solar beam skips its charge turn. moonlight, morning sun, and synthesis heal 2/3 of the user's max HP. Pokémon with chlorophyll have doubled original Speed. Pokémon with forecast become fire. Pokémon with leaf guard are not affected by major status effects. Pokémon with flower gift change form; every Pokémon on their side of the field have their original Attack and Special Attack increased by 50%. Pokémon with dry skin lose 1/8 max HP at the end of each turn. Pokémon with solar power have their original Special Attack raised by 50% but lose 1/8 their max HP at the end of each turn.
effect_entry_ko: 5턴 동안 햇살을 강하게 해서 불꽃타입 기술의 위력을 올린다.

name: Crunch
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 20% chance to lower the target's Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 날카로운 이빨로 상대를 깨물어 부숴서 공격한다. 상대의 방어를 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Mirror Coat
effect_entry: Targets the last opposing Pokémon to hit the user with a special move this turn. Inflicts twice the damage that move did to the user. If there is no eligible target, this move will fail. Type immunity applies, but other type effects are ignored. This move cannot be copied by mirror move, nor selected by assist or metronome.
effect_entry_ko: 상대에게 받은 특수공격의 데미지를 2배로 만들어 그 상대에게 돌려준다.

name: Psych Up
effect_entry: Discards the user's stat changes and copies the target's. This move cannot be copied by mirror move.
effect_entry_ko: 자신에게 암시를 걸어서 능력 변화 상태를 상대와 똑같은 상태로 만든다.

name: Extreme Speed
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 눈에 보이지 않는 굉장한 속도로 상대에게 돌진하여 공격한다. 반드시 선제공격을 할 수 있다.

name: Ancient Power
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to raise all of the user's stats one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 원시의 힘으로 공격한다. 자신의 모든 능력이 오를 때가 있다.

name: Shadow Ball
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 20% chance to lower the target's Special Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 까만 그림자의 덩어리를 내던져서 공격한다. 상대의 특수방어를 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Future Sight
effect_entry: Inflicts typeless regular damage at the end of the third turn, starting with this one. This move cannot score a critical hit. If the target switches out, its replacement will be hit instead. Damage is calculated at the time this move is used; stat changes and switching out during the delay won't change the damage inflicted. No move with this effect can be used against the same target again until after the end of the third turn. This effect breaks through wonder guard. If the target is protected by protect or detect on the turn this move is used, this move will fail. However, the damage on the third turn will break through protection. The damage is applied at the end of the turn, so it ignores endure and focus sash. This move cannot be copied by mirror move.
effect_entry_ko: 기술을 사용한 2턴 뒤에 상대에게 염동력의 덩어리를 보내어 공격한다.

name: Rock Smash
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 50% chance to lower the target's Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 펀치로 공격한다. 상대의 방어를 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다. 바위를 깰 수도 있다.

name: Whirlpool
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. For the next 2–5 turns, the target cannot leave the field and is damaged for 1/16 its max HP at the end of each turn. The user continues to use other moves during this time. If the user leaves the field, this effect ends. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use. If the target is in the first turn of dive, this move will hit with double power.
effect_entry_ko: 세차게 소용돌이치는 물속에 4-5턴 동안 상대를 가두어 공격한다.

name: Beat Up
effect_entry: Inflicts typeless regular damage. Every Pokémon in the user's party, excepting those that have fainted or have a major status effect, attacks the target. Calculated stats are ignored; the base stats for the target and assorted attackers are used instead. The random factor in the damage formula is not used. dark Pokémon still get STAB. This effect breaks through wonder guard.
effect_entry_ko: 같은 편 전원이 공격한다. 동료 포켓몬이 많을수록 기술의 공격 횟수가 증가한다.

name: Fake Out
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Causes the target to flinch. Can only be used on the user's first turn after entering the field.
effect_entry_ko: 선제공격으로 상대를 풀죽게 한다. 배틀에 나가서 바로 쓰지 않으면 성공할 수 없다.

name: Uproar
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User is forced to use this move for 2–5 turns, selected at random. All Pokémon on the field wake up, and none can fall to sleep until the lock-in ends. Pokémon cannot use rest during this effect. This move cannot be selected by sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 3턴 동안 소란 피워 공격한다. 그 동안은 아무도 잠들지 않게 된다.

name: Stockpile
effect_entry: Raises the user's Defense and Special Defense by one stage each. Stores energy for use with spit up and swallow. Up to three levels of energy can be stored, and all are lost if the user leaves the field. Energy is still stored even if the stat boosts cannot be applied. If the user uses baton pass, the stat boosts are passed as normal, but the stored energy is not.
effect_entry_ko: 힘을 비축해서 자신의 방어와 특수방어를 올린다. 최대 3회까지 비축할 수 있다.

name: Spit Up
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power is equal to 100 times the amount of energy stored by stockpile. Ignores the random factor in the damage formula. Stored energy is consumed, and the user's Defense and Special Defense are reset to what they would be if stockpile had not been used. If the user has no energy stored, this move will fail. This move cannot be copied by mirror move.
effect_entry_ko: 비축된 힘을 상대에게 부딪쳐서 공격한다. 비축된 만큼 위력이 올라간다.

name: Swallow
effect_entry: Heals the user depending on the amount of energy stored by stockpile: 1/4 its max HP after one use, 1/2 its max HP after two uses, or fully after three uses. Stored energy is consumed, and the user's Defense and Special Defense are reset to what they would be if stockpile had not been used. If the user has no energy stored, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 비축된 힘을 꿀꺽해서 자신의 HP를 회복한다. 비축된 만큼 회복한다.

name: Heat Wave
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to burn the target.
effect_entry_ko: 뜨거운 숨결을 상대에게 내뿜어 공격한다. 화상 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Hail
effect_entry: Changes the weather to hail for five turns, during which non-ice Pokémon are damaged for 1/16 their max HP at the end of every turn. If the user is holding icy rock, this effect lasts for eight turns. blizzard has 100% accuracy. If the target has used detect or protect, blizzard has a (100 - accuracy)% chance to break through the protection. moonlight, morning sun, and synthesis heal only 1/4 of the user's max HP. Pokémon with snow cloak are exempt from this effect's damage.
effect_entry_ko: 5턴 동안 싸라기눈을 내리게 해 얼음타입이 아닌 포켓몬 모두에게 데미지를 준다.

name: Torment
effect_entry: Prevents the target from attempting to use the same move twice in a row. When the target leaves the field, this effect ends. If the target is forced to attempt a repeated move due to choice band, choice scarf, choice specs, disable, encore, taunt, only having PP remaining for one move, or any other effect, the target will use struggle instead. The target is then free to use the forced move next turn, as it didn't use that move this turn.
effect_entry_ko: 상대에게 트집을 잡아서 똑같은 기술을 2회 연속으로 쓸 수 없게 한다.

name: Flatter
effect_entry: Raises the target's Special Attack by one stage, then confuses it.
effect_entry_ko: 상대를 부추겨서 혼란시킨다. 동시에 상대의 특수공격도 올라가 버린다.

name: Will-O-Wisp
effect_entry: Burns the target.
effect_entry_ko: 으스스하고 괴상한 불꽃을 쏘아 상대를 화상 상태로 만든다.

name: Memento
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Attack and Special Attack by two stages. User faints.
effect_entry_ko: 자신은 기절하게 되지만 그 대신 상대의 공격과 특수공격을 크게 떨어뜨린다.

name: Facade
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the user is burned, paralyzed, or poisoned, this move has double power.
effect_entry_ko: 자신이 독, 마비, 화상 상태일 때 날리면 기술의 위력이 2배가 된다.

name: Focus Punch
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the user takes damage this turn before hitting, this move will fail. This move cannot be copied by mirror move, nor selected by assist, metronome, or sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 정신력을 높여 펀치를 날린다. 기술을 쓰기 전에 공격을 받으면 실패한다.

name: Smelling Salts
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target is paralyzed, this move has double power, and the target is cured of its paralysis.
effect_entry_ko: 마비 상태의 상대에게는 위력이 2배가 되지만 대신 상대의 마비가 풀린다.

name: Follow Me
effect_entry: Until the end of this turn, any moves that opposing Pokémon target solely at the user's ally will instead target the user. If both Pokémon on the same side of the field use this move on the same turn, the Pokémon that uses it last will become the target. This effect takes priority over lightning rod and storm drain. If the user's ally switches out, opposing Pokémon may still hit it with pursuit. This move cannot be selected by assist or metronome.
effect_entry_ko: 자신에게 주목시켜 상대로부터의 공격을 모두 자신에게 향하게 한다.

name: Nature Power
effect_entry: Uses another move chosen according to the terrain. Terrain          | Selected move ------------------------- | ------------------ Building         | tri attack Cave           | rock slide Deep water        | hydro pump Desert          | earthquake Grass           | seed bomb Mountain         | rock slide Road           | earthquake Shallow water       | hydro pump Snow           | blizzard Tall grass        | seed bomb electric terrain | thunderbolt grassy terrain  | energy ball misty terrain  | moonblast In Pokémon Battle Revolution: Terrain    | Selected move -------------- | ------------------ Courtyard   | tri attack Crystal    | rock slide Gateway    | hydro pump Magma     | rock slide Main Street  | tri attack Neon      | tri attack Stargazer   | rock slide Sunny Park   | seed bomb Sunset     | earthquake Waterfall   | seed bomb This move cannot be copied by mirror move.
effect_entry_ko: 자연의 힘으로 공격한다. 사용하는 장소에 따라 나오는 기술이 변화한다.

name: Charge
effect_entry: Raises the user's Special Defense by one stage. If the user uses an electric move next turn, its power will be doubled.
effect_entry_ko: 다음 턴에 쓸 전기타입 기술의 위력을 올린다. 자신의 특수방어도 올라간다.

name: Taunt
effect_entry: Target is forced to only use damaging moves for the next 3–5 turns, selected at random. Moves that select other moves not known in advance do not count as damaging. assist, copycat, me first, metronome, mirror move, and sleep talk do not directly inflict damage and thus may not be used. bide, counter, endeavor, metal burst, and mirror coat are allowed.
effect_entry_ko: 상대를 화나게 한다. 3턴 동안 상대는 데미지를 주는 기술밖에 쓸 수 없게 된다.

name: Helping Hand
effect_entry: Boosts the power of the target's moves by 50% until the end of this turn. This move cannot be copied by mirror move, nor selected by assist or metronome.
effect_entry_ko: 동료를 돕는다. 도움받은 포켓몬이 쓰는 기술의 위력은 여느 때보다 커진다.

name: Trick
effect_entry: User and target permanently swap held items. Works even if one of the Pokémon isn't holding anything. If either Pokémon is holding mail, this move will fail. If either Pokémon has multitype or sticky hold, this move will fail. If this move results in a Pokémon obtaining choice band, choice scarf, or choice specs, and that Pokémon was the latter of the pair to move this turn, then the move it used this turn becomes its chosen forced move. This applies even if both Pokémon had a choice item before this move was used. If the first of the two Pokémon gains a choice item, it may select whatever choice move it wishes next turn. Neither the user nor the target can recover its item with recycle. This move cannot be selected by assist or metronome.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 빈틈을 노려 자신과 상대가 지닌 물건을 교환한다.

name: Role Play
effect_entry: User's ability is replaced with the target's until the user leaves the field. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers. If the target has flower gift, forecast, illusion, imposter, multitype, stance change, trace, wonder guard, or zen mode, this move will fail. This move cannot be copied by mirror move.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 역할을 하여 자신도 상대와 같은 특성으로 변화한다.

name: Wish
effect_entry: At the end of the next turn, user will be healed for half its max HP. If the user is switched out, its replacement will be healed instead for half of the user's max HP. If the user faints or is forcefully switched by roar or whirlwind, this effect will not activate.
effect_entry_ko: 다음 턴에 자신의 HP를 최대 HP의 절반만큼 회복한다.

name: Assist
effect_entry: Uses a move from another Pokémon in the user's party, both selected at random. Moves from fainted Pokémon can be used. If there are no eligible Pokémon or moves, this move will fail. This move will not select assist, chatter, circle throw, copycat, counter, covet, destiny bond, detect, dig, dive, dragon tail, endure, feint, fly focus punch, follow me, helping hand, me first, metronome, mimic, mirror coat, mirror move, phantom force protect, quick guard, roar shadow force, sketch, sleep talk, snatch, struggle, switcheroo, thief, trick, whirlwind, or wide guard. This move cannot be copied by mirror move, nor selected by metronome or sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 서둘러서 같은 편의 도움을 받아 교대 포켓몬이 기억하고 있는 기술 중 하나를 쓴다.

name: Ingrain
effect_entry: Prevents the user from switching out. User regains 1/16 of its max HP at the end of every turn. If the user was immune to ground attacks, it will now take normal damage from them. roar and whirlwind will not affect the user. The user cannot use magnet rise. The user may still use u turn to leave the field. This effect can be passed with baton pass.
effect_entry_ko: 대지에 뿌리를 박아 매 턴마다 자신의 HP를 회복한다. 뿌리 박고 있으므로 교체할 수 없다.

name: Superpower
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage, then lowers the user's Attack and Defense by one stage each.
effect_entry_ko: 엄청난 힘을 발휘하여 상대를 공격한다. 자신의 공격과 방어가 떨어진다.

name: Magic Coat
effect_entry: The first non-damaging move targeting the user this turn that inflicts major status effects, stat changes, or trapping effects will be reflected at its user. defog, memento, and teeter dance are not reflected. attract, flatter, gastro acid, leech seed, swagger, worry seed, and yawn are reflected. This move cannot be copied by mirror move.
effect_entry_ko: 상대가 상태 이상이 되는 기술이나 씨뿌리기 등을 썼을 때 되받아친다.

name: Recycle
effect_entry: User recovers the last item consumed by the user or a Pokémon in its position on the field. The item must be used again before it can be recovered by this move again. If the user is holding an item, this move fails. Items taken or given away by covet, knock off, switcheroo, thief, or trick may not be recovered.
effect_entry_ko: 배틀 중에 사용하여 없어진 자신의 지닌 물건을 재생시켜 사용할 수 있게 한다.

name: Revenge
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target damaged the user this turn and was the last to do so, this move has double power. pain split does not count as damaging the user.
effect_entry_ko: 상대에게 기술을 받으면 그 상대에게 주는 데미지가 2배가 된다.

name: Brick Break
effect_entry: Destroys any light screen or reflect on the target's side of the field, then inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 수도로 기세 좋게 내려쳐서 상대를 공격한다. 빛의장막이나 리플렉터도 파괴할 수 있다.

name: Yawn
effect_entry: Puts the target to sleep at the end of the next turn. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers. If the target leaves the field, this effect is canceled. If the target has a status effect when this move is used, this move will fail.
