If the target is protected by safeguard when this move is used, this move will fail. insomnia and vital spirit prevent the sleep if the target has either at the end of the next turn, but will not cause this move to fail on use.
effect_entry_ko: 큰 하품으로 졸음을 유도한다. 다음 턴에 상대를 잠듦 상태로 만든다.

name: Knock Off
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Target loses its held item. Neither the user nor the target can recover its item with recycle. If the target has multitype or sticky hold, it will take damage but not lose its item.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 지닌 물건을 탁 쳐서 떨어뜨려 배틀이 끝날 때까지 사용할 수 없게 한다. 물건을 가진 상대에게는 데미지를 더 준다.

name: Endeavor
effect_entry: Inflicts exactly enough damage to lower the target's HP to equal the user's. If the target's HP is not higher than the user's, this move has no effect. Type immunity applies, but other type effects are ignored. This effect counts as damage for moves that respond to damage.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 HP가 자신의 HP와 같아지도록 데미지를 준다.

name: Eruption
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power increases with the user's remaining HP and is given by `150 * HP / max HP`, to a maximum of 150 when the user has full HP.
effect_entry_ko: 분노를 폭발시켜 상대를 공격한다. 자신의 HP가 적을수록 기술의 위력이 떨어진다.

name: Skill Swap
effect_entry: User and target switch abilities. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers. If either Pokémon has multitype or wonder guard, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 초능력으로 자신의 특성과 상대의 특성을 바꾼다.

name: Imprison
effect_entry: Prevents any Pokémon on the opposing side of the field from using any move the user knows until the user leaves the field. This effect is live; if the user obtains new moves while on the field, these moves become restricted. If no opposing Pokémon knows any of the user's moves when this move is used, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 상대가 자신과 같은 기술을 기억하고 있으면 상대만 그 기술을 사용할 수 없게 한다.

name: Refresh
effect_entry: Removes a burn, paralysis, or poison from the user.
effect_entry_ko: 몸을 쉬게 하여 자신이 입은 독, 마비, 화상의 상태 이상을 치료한다.

name: Grudge
effect_entry: If the user faints before it next acts, the move that fainted it will have its PP dropped to 0. End-of-turn damage does not trigger this effect.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 기술로 기절하면 원념을 담아 그 기술의 PP를 0으로 만든다.

name: Snatch
effect_entry: The next time a Pokémon uses a beneficial move on itself or itself and its ally this turn, the user of this move will steal the move and use it itself. Moves which may be stolen by this move are identified by the "snatchable" flag. If two Pokémon use this move on the same turn, the faster Pokémon will steal the first beneficial move, and the slower Pokémon will then steal it again—thus, only the slowest Pokémon using this move ultimately gains a stolen move's effect. If the user steals psych up, it will target the Pokémon that used psych up. If the user was the original target of psych up, and the Pokémon that originally used it's affected by pressure, it will only lose 1 PP. This move cannot be copied by mirror move, nor selected by assist or metronome.
effect_entry_ko: 상대가 사용하려고 한 회복 기술이나 능력 변화의 기술을 빼앗아 자신에게 쓴다.

name: Secret Power
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to inflict an effect chosen according to the terrain. Terrain    | Effect -------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------- Building    | Paralyzes target Cave      | Makes target flinch Deep water   | Lowers target's Attack by one stage Desert     | Lowers target's accuracy by one stage Grass     | Puts target to sleep Mountain    | Makes target flinch Road      | Lowers target's accuracy by one stage Shallow water | Lowers target's Attack by one stage Snow      | Freezes target Tall grass   | Puts target to sleep In Pokémon Battle Revolution: Terrain    | Effect -------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------- Courtyard   | Paralyzes target Crystal    | Makes target flinch Gateway    | Lowers target's Attack by one stage Magma     | Makes target flinch Main Street  | Paralyzes target Neon      | Paralyzes target Stargazer   | Makes target flinch Sunny Park   | Puts target to sleep Sunset     | Lowers target's accuracy by one stage Waterfall   | Puts target to sleep
effect_entry_ko: 비밀의 힘으로 상대를 공격한다. 사용 장소에 따라 추가 효과가 변화한다.

name: Dive
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User dives underwater for one turn, becoming immune to attack, and hits on the second turn. During the immune turn, surf, and whirlpool still hit the user normally, and their power is doubled if appropriate. The user may be hit during its immune turn if under the effect of lock on, mind reader, or no guard. This move cannot be selected by sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 1턴째에 잠수했다가 2턴째에 떠올라 공격한다.

name: Arm Thrust
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits 2–5 times in one turn. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use.
effect_entry_ko: 펼친 양손으로 상대를 번갈아 쳐서 공격한다. 2-5회 동안 연속으로 쓴다.

name: Camouflage
effect_entry: User's type changes according to the terrain. Terrain    | New type -------------- | -------------- Building    | normal Cave      | rock Desert     | ground Grass     | grass Mountain    | rock Ocean     | water Pond      | water Road      | ground Snow      | ice Tall grass   | grass In Pokémon Battle Revolution: Terrain    | New type -------------- | -------------- Courtyard   | normal Crystal    | rock Gateway    | water Magma     | rock Main Street  | normal Neon      | normal Stargazer   | rock Sunny Park   | grass Sunset     | ground Waterfall   | grass
effect_entry_ko: 물가나 풀밭, 동굴 등 있는 장소에 맞춰서 자신의 타입을 바꾼다.

name: Tail Glow
effect_entry: Raises the user's Special Attack by three stages.
effect_entry_ko: 깜빡거리는 빛을 바라보고 자신의 정신을 통일하여 특수공격을 매우 크게 올린다.

name: Luster Purge
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 50% chance to lower the target's Special Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 눈부신 빛을 발산하여 공격한다. 상대의 특수방어를 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Mist Ball
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 50% chance to lower the target's Special Attack by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 안개의 깃털로 둘러싸 공격한다. 상대의 특수공격을 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Feather Dance
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Attack by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 깃털을 흩뿌려 상대의 몸에 휘감는다. 상대의 공격을 크게 떨어뜨린다.

name: Teeter Dance
effect_entry: Confuses all targets.
effect_entry_ko: 흔들흔들 댄스를 춰서 주위에 있는 포켓몬을 혼란 상태로 만든다.

name: Blaze Kick
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move. Has a 10% chance to burn the target.
effect_entry_ko: 공격한 상대를 화상 상태로 만들 때가 있다. 급소에도 맞기 쉽다.

name: Mud Sport
effect_entry: electric moves inflict half damage, regardless of target. If the user leaves the field, this effect ends.
effect_entry_ko: 주위를 진흙투성이로 만든다. 5턴 동안 전기타입의 기술을 약하게 한다.

name: Ice Ball
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User is forced to use this move for five turns. Power doubles every time this move is used in succession to a maximum of 16x, and resets to normal after the lock-in ends. If this move misses or becomes unusable, the lock-in ends. If the user has used defense curl since entering the field, this move has double power.
effect_entry_ko: 5턴 동안 구르기를 반복하여 상대를 공격한다. 기술이 맞을 때마다 위력이 올라간다.

name: Needle Arm
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 바늘팔을 세차게 흔들어 공격한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: Slack Off
effect_entry: Heals the user for half its max HP.
effect_entry_ko: 게으름 피우며 쉰다. 자신의 HP를 최대 HP의 절반만큼 회복한다.

name: Hyper Voice
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 시끄럽게 울려서 큰 진동을 상대에게 전달하여 공격한다.

name: Poison Fang
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 50% chance to badly poison the target.
effect_entry_ko: 독이 있는 이빨로 상대를 물어서 공격한다. 맹독을 주입할 때가 있다.

name: Crush Claw
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 50% chance to lower the target's Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 단단하고 날카로운 손톱으로 베어 갈라서 공격한다. 상대의 방어를 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Blast Burn
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User loses its next turn to "recharge", and cannot attack or switch out during that turn.
effect_entry_ko: 폭발하는 불꽃으로 상대를 태워서 공격한다. 다음 턴은 움직일 수 없다.

name: Hydro Cannon
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User loses its next turn to "recharge", and cannot attack or switch out during that turn.
effect_entry_ko: 물의 대포를 상대에게 발사해서 공격한다. 다음 턴은 움직일 수 없다.

name: Meteor Mash
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 20% chance to raise the user's Attack one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 혜성과 같은 펀치를 날려서 상대를 공격한다. 자신의 공격이 올라갈 때가 있다.

name: Astonish
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 큰 소리 등으로 불시에 놀래켜서 공격한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: Weather Ball
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If a weather move is active, this move has double power, and its type becomes the type of the weather move. shadow sky is typeless for the purposes of this move.
effect_entry_ko: 사용했을 때의 날씨에 따라서 기술 타입과 위력이 바뀐다.

name: Aromatherapy
effect_entry: Removes major status effects and confusion from every Pokémon in the user's party.
effect_entry_ko: 기분 좋은 평온한 향기를 맡게 하여 같은 편 모두의 상태 이상을 회복한다.

name: Fake Tears
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Special Defense by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 우는 척을 하며 눈물을 흘린다. 난처하게 만들어 상대의 특수방어를 크게 떨어뜨린다.

name: Air Cutter
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move.
effect_entry_ko: 날카로운 바람으로 상대를 베어 공격한다. 급소에 맞기 쉽다.

name: Overheat
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage, then lowers the user's Special Attack by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 풀 파워로 상대를 공격한다. 쓰면 반동으로 자신의 특수공격이 크게 떨어진다.

name: Odor Sleuth
effect_entry: Resets the target's evasion to normal and prevents any further boosting until the target leaves the field. A ghost under this effect takes normal damage from normal and fighting moves. This move itself ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers.
effect_entry_ko: 고스트타입에 효과가 없는 기술이나 회피율이 높은 상대라 할지라도 공격이 맞게 된다.

name: Rock Tomb
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 100% chance to lower the target's Speed by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 암석을 내던져서 공격한다. 상대의 움직임을 봉인함으로써 스피드를 떨어뜨린다.

name: Silver Wind
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to raise all of the user's stats one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 바람에 날개 가루를 날려서 상대를 공격한다. 자신의 모든 능력이 올라갈 때가 있다.

name: Metal Sound
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Special Defense by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 금속을 긁을 때 나는 듯한 싫은 소리를 들려준다. 상대의 특수방어를 크게 떨어뜨린다.

name: Grass Whistle
effect_entry: Puts the target to sleep.
effect_entry_ko: 기분 좋은 피리 소리를 들려주어 상대를 잠듦 상태로 만든다.

name: Tickle
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Attack and Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 몸을 간질여 웃게 만들어서 상대의 공격과 방어를 떨어뜨린다.

name: Cosmic Power
effect_entry: Raises the user's Defense and Special Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 우주로부터 신비한 힘을 손에 넣음으로써 자신의 방어와 특수방어를 올린다.

name: Water Spout
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power increases with the user's remaining HP and is given by `150 * HP / max HP`, to a maximum of 150 when the user has full HP.
effect_entry_ko: 바닷물을 내뿜어 공격한다. 자신의 HP가 적을수록 기술의 위력이 떨어진다.

name: Signal Beam
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to confuse the target.
effect_entry_ko: 이상한 빛을 발사해서 공격한다. 상대를 혼란시킬 때가 있다.

name: Shadow Punch
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers.
effect_entry_ko: 그림자에 섞여 펀치를 날린다. 공격은 반드시 명중한다.

name: Extrasensory
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 보이지 않는 이상한 힘을 보내어 공격한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: Sky Uppercut
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. This move can hit Pokémon under the effect of bounce, fly, or sky drop.
effect_entry_ko: 하늘을 향하는 듯한 높은 업퍼로 상대를 밀어올려 공격한다.

name: Sand Tomb
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. For the next 2–5 turns, the target cannot leave the field and is damaged for 1/16 its max HP at the end of each turn. The user continues to use other moves during this time. If the user leaves the field, this effect ends. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use. rapid spin cancels this effect.
effect_entry_ko: 세차게 불어대는 모래바람 속에 4-5턴 동안 상대를 가두어 공격한다.

name: Sheer Cold
effect_entry: Inflicts damage equal to the target's max HP. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers. This move's accuracy is 30% plus 1% for each level the user is higher than the target. If the user is a lower level than the target, this move will fail. Because this move inflicts a specific and finite amount of damage, endure still prevents the target from fainting. The effects of lock on, mind reader, and no guard still apply, as long as the user is equal or higher level than the target. However, they will not give this move a chance to break through detect or protect.
effect_entry_ko: 절대영도의 추위로 상대를 공격한다. 맞으면 일격에 기절한다.

name: Muddy Water
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to lower the target's accuracy by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 탁해진 물을 상대에게 발사하여 공격한다. 명중률을 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Bullet Seed
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits 2–5 times in one turn. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use.
effect_entry_ko: 씨앗을 기세 좋게 상대에게 발사하여 공격한다. 2-5회 동안 연속으로 쓴다.

name: Aerial Ace
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers.
effect_entry_ko: 재빠른 움직임으로 상대를 농락해 벤다. 공격은 반드시 명중한다.

name: Icicle Spear
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits 2–5 times in one turn. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use.
effect_entry_ko: 날카로운 고드름을 상대에게 발사하여 공격한다. 2-5회 동안 연속으로 쓴다.

name: Iron Defense
effect_entry: Raises the user's Defense by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 피부를 쇠처럼 단단하게 함으로써 자신의 방어를 크게 올린다.

name: Block
effect_entry: The target cannot switch out normally. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers. This effect ends when the user leaves the field. The target may still escape by using baton pass, u turn, or a shed shell. Both the user and the target pass on this effect with baton pass.
effect_entry_ko: 양팔을 벌려 막아서서 상대의 도주로를 가로막아 도망칠 수 없게 한다.

name: Howl
effect_entry: Raises the user's Attack by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 큰 소리로 짖고 기합을 높여 아군 전체의 공격을 올린다.

name: Dragon Claw
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 날카롭고 뾰족한 거대한 발톱으로 상대를 베어 갈라서 공격한다.

name: Frenzy Plant
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User loses its next turn to "recharge", and cannot attack or switch out during that turn.
effect_entry_ko: 큰 나무로 상대를 힘껏 쳐서 공격한다. 다음 턴은 움직일 수 없게 된다.

name: Bulk Up
effect_entry: Raises the user's Attack and Defense by one stage each.
effect_entry_ko: 몸에 힘을 담아 근육을 두껍게 해서 자신의 공격과 방어를 올린다.

name: Bounce
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User bounces high into the air for one turn, becoming immune to attack, and hits on the second turn. Has a 30% chance to paralyze the target. During the immune turn, gust, hurricane, sky uppercut, smack down, thunder, and twister still hit the user normally. gust and twister also have double power against the user. The damage from hail and sandstorm still applies during the immune turn. The user may be hit during its immune turn if under the effect of lock on, mind reader, or no guard. This move cannot be used while gravity is in effect. This move cannot be selected by sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 하늘 높이 뛰어올라 2턴째에 상대를 공격한다. 마비 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Mud Shot
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 100% chance to lower the target's Speed by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 진흙 덩어리를 상대에게 내던져서 공격한다. 동시에 상대의 스피드를 떨어뜨린다.

name: Poison Tail
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move. Has a 10% chance to poison the target.
effect_entry_ko: 꼬리로 때린다. 독 상태로 만들 때가 있고 급소에도 맞기 쉽다.

name: Covet
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target is holding an item and the user is not, the user will permanently take the item. Damage is still inflicted if an item cannot be taken. Pokémon with sticky hold or multitype are immune to the item theft effect. The target cannot recover its item with recycle. This move cannot be selected by assist or metronome.
effect_entry_ko: 귀엽게 애교부리며 상대에게 다가가 지니고 있는 도구를 뺏는다.

name: Volt Tackle
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User takes 1/3 the damage it inflicts in recoil. Has a 10% chance to paralyze the target.
effect_entry_ko: 전기를 한데 모아 돌진한다. 자신도 상당한 데미지를 입는다. 마비 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Magical Leaf
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers.
effect_entry_ko: 상대를 추적하는 이상한 잎사귀를 흩뿌린다. 공격은 반드시 명중한다.

name: Water Sport
effect_entry: fire moves inflict half damage, regardless of target. If the user leaves the field, this effect ends.
effect_entry_ko: 주위를 물로 흠뻑 젖게 만든다. 5턴 동안 불꽃타입의 기술을 약하게 한다.

name: Calm Mind
effect_entry: Raises the user's Special Attack and Special Defense by one stage each.
effect_entry_ko: 조용히 정신을 통일하고 마음을 가라앉혀서 자신의 특수공격과 특수방어를 올린다.

name: Leaf Blade
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move.
effect_entry_ko: 잎사귀를 칼처럼 이용해 상대를 베어 공격한다. 급소에 맞기 쉽다.

name: Dragon Dance
effect_entry: Raises the user's Attack and Speed by one stage each.
effect_entry_ko: 신비롭고 힘센 춤을 격렬하게 춘다. 자신의 공격과 스피드를 올린다.

name: Rock Blast
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits 2–5 times in one turn. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use.
effect_entry_ko: 단단한 암석을 상대에게 발사하여 공격한다. 2-5회 동안 연속으로 쓴다.

name: Shock Wave
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers.
effect_entry_ko: 전격을 재빠르게 상대에게 날린다. 공격은 반드시 명중한다.

name: Water Pulse
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 20% chance to confuse the target.
effect_entry_ko: 물의 진동을 상대에게 가하여 공격한다. 상대를 혼란시킬 때가 있다.

name: Doom Desire
effect_entry: Inflicts typeless regular damage at the end of the third turn, starting with this one. This move cannot score a critical hit. If the target switches out, its replacement will be hit instead. Damage is calculated at the time this move is used; stat changes and switching out during the delay won't change the damage inflicted. No move with this effect can be used against the same target again until after the end of the third turn. This effect breaks through wonder guard. If the target is protected by protect or detect on the turn this move is used, this move will fail. However, the damage on the third turn will break through protection. The damage is applied at the end of the turn, so it ignores endure and focus sash. This move cannot be copied by mirror move.
effect_entry_ko: 기술을 사용한 2턴 뒤에 무수한 빛의 다발이 상대를 공격한다.

name: Psycho Boost
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage, then lowers the user's Special Attack by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 풀 파워로 상대를 공격한다. 쓰면 반동으로 자신의 특수공격이 크게 떨어진다.

name: Roost
effect_entry: Heals the user for half its max HP. If the user is flying, its flying type is ignored until the end of this turn.
effect_entry_ko: 땅에 내려와 몸을 쉬게 한다. 최대 HP의 절반만큼 HP를 회복한다.

name: Gravity
effect_entry: For five turns (including this one), all immunities to ground moves are disabled. For the duration of this effect, the evasion of every Pokémon on the field is lowered by two stages. Cancels the effects of bounce, fly, and sky drop. Specifically, flying Pokémon and those with levitate or that have used magnet rise are no longer immune to ground attacks, arena trap, spikes, or toxic spikes. bounce, fly, sky drop, high jump kick, jump kick, and splash cannot be used while this move is in effect. *Bug*: If this move is used during a double or triple battle while Pokémon are under the effect of sky drop, Sky Drop's effect is not correctly canceled on its target, and it remains high in the air indefinitely. As Sky Drop prevents the target from acting, the only way to subsequently remove it from the field is to faint it.
effect_entry_ko: 5턴 동안 중력을 강하게 해서 부유나 하늘을 나는 기술을 사용할 수 없게 한다.

name: Miracle Eye
effect_entry: Resets the target's evasion to normal and prevents any further boosting until the target leaves the field. A dark Pokémon under this effect takes normal damage from psychic moves. This move itself ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers.
effect_entry_ko: 악타입에 효과가 없는 기술이나 회피율이 높은 상대라 할지라도 공격이 맞게 된다.

name: Wake-Up Slap
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target is sleeping, this move has double power, and the target wakes up.
effect_entry_ko: 잠듦 상태의 상대에게 큰 데미지를 준다. 대신 상대는 잠에서 깬다.

name: Hammer Arm
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage, then lowers the user's Speed by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 강하고 무거운 주먹을 휘둘러 데미지를 준다. 자신의 스피드가 떨어진다.

name: Gyro Ball
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power increases with the target's current Speed compared to the user, given by `1 + 25 * target Speed / user Speed`, capped at 150.
effect_entry_ko: 몸을 고속으로 회전시켜 몸통박치기한다. 상대보다 스피드가 낮을수록 위력은 올라간다.

name: Healing Wish
effect_entry: User faints. Its replacement's HP is fully restored, and any major status effect is removed. If the replacement Pokémon is immediately fainted by a switch-in effect, the next replacement is healed by this move instead.
effect_entry_ko: 자신은 기절하지만 교대하여 나오는 포켓몬의 상태 이상과 HP를 회복한다.

name: Brine
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target has less than half its max HP remaining, this move has double power.
effect_entry_ko: 상대가 HP의 절반 정도 상처를 입고 있으면 기술의 위력이 2배가 된다.

name: Natural Gift
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power and type are determined by the user's held berry. The berry is consumed. If the user is not holding a berry, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 나무열매에서 힘을 얻어 공격한다. 지니게 한 나무열매에 따라 기술의 타입과 위력이 바뀐다.

name: Feint
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Removes the effects of detect or protect from the target before hitting. This move cannot be copied by mirror move, nor selected by assist or metronome.
effect_entry_ko: 방어나 판별을 하고 있는 상대에게 공격할 수 있다. 방어 효과를 해제시킨다.

name: Pluck
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target is holding a berry, this move has double power, and the user takes the berry and uses it immediately. If the target is holding a jaboca berry or rowap berry, the berry is still removed, but has no effect. If this move is super effective and the target is holding a berry that can reduce this move's damage, it will do so, and will not be stolen.
effect_entry_ko: 부리로 공격한다. 상대가 나무열매를 지니고 있을 때 먹어서 나무열매의 효과를 받을 수 있다.

name: Tailwind
effect_entry: For the next three turns, all Pokémon on the user's side of the field have their original Speed doubled. This effect remains if the user leaves the field.
effect_entry_ko: 세차게 불어대는 바람의 소용돌이를 만들어 4턴 동안 같은 편 모두의 스피드를 올린다.

name: Acupressure
effect_entry: Raises one of the target's stats by two stages. The raised stat is chosen at random from any stats that can be raised by two stages. If no stat is eligible, this move will fail. If the target has a substitute, this move will have no effect, even if the user is the target. This move cannot be copied by mirror move.
effect_entry_ko: 경혈을 눌러 몸을 활성화시킨다. 능력 중 하나를 크게 올린다.

name: Metal Burst
effect_entry: Targets the last opposing Pokémon to hit the user with a damaging move this turn. Inflicts 1.5× the damage that move did to the user. If there is no eligible target, this move will fail. Type immunity applies, but other type effects are ignored.
effect_entry_ko: 기술을 쓰기 전에 마지막으로 받은 기술의 데미지를 늘려서 기술을 쓴 상대에게 돌려준다.

name: U-turn
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage, then the user immediately switches out, and the trainer selects a replacement Pokémon from the party. If the target faints from this attack, the user's trainer selects the new Pokémon to send out first. If the user is the last Pokémon in its party that can battle, it will not switch out. The user may be hit by pursuit when it switches out, if it has been targeted and pursuit has not yet been used. This move may be used even if the user is under the effect of ingrain. ingrain's effect will end.
effect_entry_ko: 공격한 뒤 굉장한 스피드로 돌아와서 교대 포켓몬과 교체한다.

name: Close Combat
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage, then lowers the user's Defense and Special Defense by one stage each.
effect_entry_ko: 방어를 포기하고 상대 깊숙이 돌격한다. 자신의 방어와 특수방어가 떨어진다.

name: Payback
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target uses a move or switches out this turn before this move is used, this move has double power.
effect_entry_ko: 모아서 공격한다. 상대보다 뒤에 공격할 수 있으면 기술의 위력은 2배가 된다.

name: Assurance
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target takes damage this turn for any reason before this move is used, this move has double power.
effect_entry_ko: 그 턴에 상대가 이미 데미지를 입었다면 기술의 위력은 2배가 된다.

name: Embargo
effect_entry: Target cannot use its held item for five turns. If the target leaves the field, this effect ends. If a Pokémon under this effect uses bug bite or pluck on a Pokémon holding a berry, the berry is destroyed but not used. If a Pokémon under this effect uses fling, it will fail. This effect is passed by baton pass.
effect_entry_ko: 지니게 한 도구를 쓸 수 없게 한다. 트레이너도 그 포켓몬에게는 도구를 쓸 수 없다.

name: Fling
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power and type are determined by the user's held item. The item is consumed. If the user is not holding an item, or its item has no set type and power, this move will fail. This move ignores sticky hold. If the user is under the effect of embargo, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 지니게 한 도구를 재빠르게 내던져서 공격한다. 도구에 따라 위력과 효과가 바뀐다.

name: Psycho Shift
effect_entry: If the user has a major status effect and the target does not, the user's status is transferred to the target.
effect_entry_ko: 초능력으로 암시를 걸어서 자신에게 걸려 있는 상태 이상을 상대에게 옮긴다.

name: Trump Card
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power is determined by the PP remaining for this move, after its PP cost is deducted. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers. PP remaining | Power ------------ | ----: 4 or more  |  40 3      |  50 2      |  60 1      |  80 0      |  200 If this move is activated by another move, the activating move's PP is used to calculate power.
effect_entry_ko: 마지막수단의 남은 PP가 적으면 적을수록 기술의 위력이 올라간다.

name: Heal Block
effect_entry: For the next five turns, the target may not use any moves that only restore HP, and move effects that heal the target are disabled. Moves that steal HP may still be used, but will only inflict damage and not heal the target.
effect_entry_ko: 5턴 동안 기술이나 특성, 지니고 있는 도구에 의한 HP 회복을 할 수 없게 한다.

name: Wring Out
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power directly relates to the target's relative remaining HP, given by `1 + 120 * current HP / max HP`, to a maximum of 121.
effect_entry_ko: 강하게 조여 공격을 한다. 상대의 HP가 많이 남아 있을수록 위력이 올라간다.

name: Power Trick
effect_entry: The user's original Attack and Defense are swapped. This effect is passed on by baton pass.
effect_entry_ko: 초능력으로 자신의 공격과 방어의 힘을 교환한다.

name: Gastro Acid
effect_entry: The target's ability is disabled as long as it remains on the field. This effect is passed on by baton pass.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 몸에 위액을 내뱉는다. 달라붙은 위액은 상대의 특성 효과를 지운다.

name: Lucky Chant
effect_entry: For five turns, opposing Pokémon cannot score critical hits.
effect_entry_ko: 하늘을 향해 기도를 올려 상대의 공격을 급소에 맞지 않게 한다.

name: Me First
effect_entry: If the target has selected a damaging move this turn, the user will copy that move and use it against the target, with a 50% increase in power. If the target moves before the user, this move will fail. This move cannot be copied by mirror move, nor selected by assist, metronome, or sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 위력을 올려 상대가 쓰려고 하는 기술을 먼저 쓴다. 먼저 쓰지 않으면 실패한다.

name: Copycat
effect_entry: Uses the last move that was used successfully by any Pokémon, including the user. This move cannot copy itself, nor roar nor whirlwind. This move cannot be copied by mirror move, nor selected by assist, metronome, or sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 직전에 나온 기술을 흉내 내어 같은 기술을 쓴다. 기술이 나오지 않았으면 실패한다.

name: Power Swap
effect_entry: User swaps its Attack and Special Attack stat modifiers modifiers with the target.
effect_entry_ko: 초능력으로 자신과 상대의 공격과 특수공격의 능력 변화를 교체한다.

name: Guard Swap
effect_entry: User swaps its Defense and Special Defense modifiers with the target.
effect_entry_ko: 초능력으로 자신과 상대의 방어와 특수방어의 능력 변화를 교체한다.

name: Punishment
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power starts at 60 and is increased by 20 for every stage any of the target's stats has been raised, capping at 200. Accuracy and evasion modifiers do not increase this move's power.
effect_entry_ko: 능력 변화로 상대가 파워업한 만큼 기술의 위력이 올라간다.

name: Last Resort
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. This move can only be used if each of the user's other moves has been used at least once since the user entered the field. If this is the user's only move, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 배틀 중에 기억하고 있는 기술을 모두 사용하면 그때부터 쓸 수 있는 필살기이다.

name: Worry Seed
effect_entry: Changes the target's ability to insomnia. If the target's ability is truant or multitype, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 마음을 괴롭히는 씨앗을 심는다. 상대를 잠잘 수 없게 해서 특성을 불면으로 만든다.

name: Sucker Punch
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target has not selected a damaging move this turn, or if the target has already acted this turn, this move will fail. This move is not affected by iron fist.
effect_entry_ko: 상대보다 먼저 공격할 수 있다. 상대가 쓴 기술이 공격기술이 아니면 실패한다.

name: Toxic Spikes
effect_entry: Scatters poisoned spikes around the opposing field, which poison opposing Pokémon that enter the field. A second layer of these spikes may be laid down, in which case Pokémon will be badly poisoned instead. Pokémon immune to either ground moves or being poisoned are immune to this effect. Pokémon otherwise immune to ground moves are affected during gravity. If a poison Pokémon not immune to ground moves enters a field covered with poisoned spikes, the spikes are removed. rapid spin will remove this effect from its user's side of the field. defog will remove this effect from its target's side of the field. This move does not trigger synchronize, unless the Pokémon with synchronize was forced to enter the field by another effect such as roar. Pokémon entering the field due to baton pass are not affected by this effect.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 발밑에 독압정을 뿌린다. 교체로 나온 상대 포켓몬에 독을 덮어씌운다.

name: Heart Swap
effect_entry: User swaps its stat modifiers with the target.
effect_entry_ko: 초능력으로 자신과 상대에 걸려있는 능력 변화를 교체한다.

name: Aqua Ring
effect_entry: Restores 1/16 of the user's max HP at the end of each turn. If the user leaves the field, this effect ends. This effect is passed on by baton pass.
effect_entry_ko: 자신의 몸 주변을 물로 만든 베일로 덮는다. 매 턴 HP를 회복한다.

name: Magnet Rise
effect_entry: For five turns, the user is immune to ground moves. If the user is under the effect of ingrain or has levitate, this move will fail. This effect is temporarily disabled by and cannot be used during gravity. This effect is passed on by baton pass.
effect_entry_ko: 전기로 만든 자력의 힘으로 허공에 뜬다. 5턴 동안 부유할 수 있다.

name: Flare Blitz
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User takes 1/3 the damage it inflicts in recoil. Has a 10% chance to burn the target. Frozen Pokémon may use this move, in which case they will thaw.
effect_entry_ko: 불꽃을 두르고 돌진한다. 자신도 상당한 데미지를 입는다. 화상 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Force Palm
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to paralyze the target.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 몸에 충격파를 부딪쳐 공격한다. 마비 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Aura Sphere
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers.
effect_entry_ko: 몸속에서 파동의 힘을 끌어내 쏜다. 공격은 반드시 명중한다.

name: Rock Polish
effect_entry: Raises the user's Speed by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 자신의 몸을 갈아 공기의 저항을 적게 한다. 스피드를 크게 올릴 수 있다.

name: Poison Jab
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to poison the target.
effect_entry_ko: 독에 물든 촉수나 팔로 상대를 꿰찌른다. 독 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Dark Pulse
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 20% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 몸에서 악의로 가득한 무서운 오라를 발한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: Night Slash
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move.
effect_entry_ko: 순간적으로 틈을 노려 상대를 베어 버린다. 급소에 맞기 쉽다.

name: Aqua Tail
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 세차게 날뛰는 거친 파도와 같이 큰 꼬리를 흔들어서 상대를 공격한다.

name: Seed Bomb
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 단단한 껍질을 가지고 있는 큰 씨앗을 힘껏 내던져 상대를 공격한다.

name: Air Slash
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 하늘까지 베어 가르는 공기의 칼날로 공격한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: X-Scissor
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 낫이나 발톱을 가위처럼 교차시키면서 상대를 베어 가른다.

name: Bug Buzz
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to lower the target's Special Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 날개의 진동으로 음파를 일으켜서 공격한다. 상대의 특수방어를 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Dragon Pulse
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 큰 입으로 충격파를 일으켜서 상대를 공격한다.

name: Dragon Rush
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 20% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 굉장한 살기로 위압하면서 몸통박치기한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: Power Gem
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 보석처럼 반짝이는 빛을 발사하여 상대를 공격한다.

name: Drain Punch
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Drains half the damage inflicted to heal the user.
effect_entry_ko: 주먹으로 상대의 힘을 흡수한다. 입힌 데미지의 절반에 해당하는 HP를 회복할 수 있다.

name: Vacuum Wave
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 주먹을 흔들어 진공의 파도를 일으킨다. 반드시 선제공격을 할 수 있다.

name: Focus Blast
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to lower the target's Special Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 기합을 높여서 혼신의 힘을 방출한다. 상대의 특수방어를 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Energy Ball
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to lower the target's Special Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 자연으로부터 모은 생명의 힘을 발사한다. 상대의 특수방어를 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Brave Bird
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User takes 1/3 the damage it inflicts in recoil.
effect_entry_ko: 날개를 접어 저공비행으로 돌격한다. 자신도 상당한 데미지를 입는다.

name: Earth Power
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to lower the target's Special Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 발밑에 대지의 힘을 방출한다. 상대의 특수방어를 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Switcheroo
effect_entry: User and target permanently swap held items. Works even if one of the Pokémon isn't holding anything. If either Pokémon is holding mail, this move will fail. If either Pokémon has multitype or sticky hold, this move will fail. If this move results in a Pokémon obtaining choice band, choice scarf, or choice specs, and that Pokémon was the latter of the pair to move this turn, then the move it used this turn becomes its chosen forced move. This applies even if both Pokémon had a choice item before this move was used. If the first of the two Pokémon gains a choice item, it may select whatever choice move it wishes next turn. Neither the user nor the target can recover its item with recycle. This move cannot be selected by assist or metronome.
effect_entry_ko: 눈에 보이지 않는 속도로 자신과 상대가 지닌 물건을 교환한다.

name: Giga Impact
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User loses its next turn to "recharge", and cannot attack or switch out during that turn.
effect_entry_ko: 가진 힘을 모두 사용해서 상대에게 돌격한다. 다음 턴은 움직일 수 없다.

name: Nasty Plot
effect_entry: Raises the user's Special Attack by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 나쁜 일을 생각해서 머리를 활성화시킨다. 자신의 특수공격을 크게 올린다.

name: Bullet Punch
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 탄환처럼 빠르고 단단한 펀치를 상대에게 날린다. 반드시 선제공격을 할 수 있다.

name: Avalanche
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target damaged the user this turn and was the last to do so, this move has double power. pain split does not count as damaging the user.
effect_entry_ko: 상대로부터 기술을 받으면 그 상대에 대해서 기술의 위력이 2배가 된다.

name: Ice Shard
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 얼음 덩어리를 순식간에 만들어 상대에게 빠르게 쏜다. 반드시 선제공격을 할 수 있다.

name: Shadow Claw
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move.
effect_entry_ko: 그림자로 만든 날카로운 발톱으로 상대를 베어 가른다. 급소에 맞기 쉽다.

name: Thunder Fang
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to paralyze the target and a separate 10% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 전기를 모은 이빨로 문다. 상대를 풀죽게 하거나 마비 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Ice Fang
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to freeze the target and a separate 10% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 냉기를 품은 이빨로 문다. 상대를 풀죽게 하거나 얼음 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Fire Fang
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to burn the target and a separate 10% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 불꽃을 두른 이빨로 문다. 상대를 풀죽게 하거나 화상 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Shadow Sneak
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 그림자를 늘려 상대의 배후에서 공격한다. 반드시 선제공격할 수 있다.

name: Mud Bomb
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to lower the target's accuracy by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 단단한 진흙구슬을 상대에게 발사하여 공격한다. 명중률을 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Psycho Cut
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move.
effect_entry_ko: 실체화시킨 마음의 칼날로 상대를 베어 가른다. 급소에 맞기 쉽다.

name: Zen Headbutt
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 20% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 사념의 힘을 이마에 모아서 공격한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: Mirror Shot
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to lower the target's accuracy by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 갈고 닦은 몸에서 섬광의 힘을 상대에게 쏜다. 명중률을 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Flash Cannon
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to lower the target's Special Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 몸의 빛을 한곳에 모아서 힘을 쏜다. 상대의 특수방어를 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Rock Climb
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 20% chance to confuse the target.
effect_entry_ko: 굉장한 기세로 상대에게 돌진하여 공격한다. 상대를 혼란시킬 때가 있다.

name: Defog
effect_entry: Lowers the target's evasion by one stage. Clears away fog. Removes the effects of mist, light screen, reflect, safeguard, spikes, stealth rock, and toxic spikes from the target's side of the field. If the target is protected by mist, it will prevent the evasion change, then be removed by this move.
effect_entry_ko: 강한 바람으로 상대의 리플렉터나 빛의장막 등을 제거한다. 회피율도 떨어뜨린다.

name: Trick Room
effect_entry: For five turns (including this one), slower Pokémon will act before faster Pokémon. Move priority is not affected. Using this move when its effect is already active will end the effect. Pokémon holding full incense, lagging tail, or quick claw and Pokémon with stall ignore this effect.
effect_entry_ko: 이상한 공간을 만든다. 5턴 동안 느린 포켓몬부터 행동할 수 있다.

name: Draco Meteor
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage, then lowers the user's Special Attack by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 천공에서 운석을 상대에게 떨어뜨린다. 사용하면 반동으로 자신의 특수공격이 크게 떨어진다.

name: Discharge
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to paralyze the target.
effect_entry_ko: 눈부신 전격으로 자신의 주위에 있는 포켓몬을 공격한다. 마비 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Lava Plume
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to burn the target.
effect_entry_ko: 새빨간 불꽃으로 자신의 주위에 있는 포켓몬을 공격한다. 화상 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Leaf Storm
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage, then lowers the user's Special Attack by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 뾰족한 잎사귀로 상대에게 바람을 일으킨다. 사용하면 반동으로 자신의 특수공격이 크게 떨어진다.

name: Power Whip
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 덩굴이나 촉수를 세차게 흔들어 상대를 힘껏 쳐서 공격한다.

name: Rock Wrecker
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User loses its next turn to "recharge", and cannot attack or switch out during that turn.
effect_entry_ko: 거대한 바위를 상대에게 발사하여 공격한다. 다음 턴은 움직일 수 없게 된다.

name: Cross Poison
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move. Has a 10% chance to poison the target.
effect_entry_ko: 독 칼날로 상대를 베어 가른다. 독 상태로 만들 때가 있고 급소에도 맞기 쉽다.

name: Gunk Shot
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to poison the target.
effect_entry_ko: 더러운 쓰레기를 상대에게 부딪쳐서 공격한다. 독 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Iron Head
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 강철과 같은 단단한 머리로 공격한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: Magnet Bomb
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Ignores accuracy and evasion modifiers.
effect_entry_ko: 상대에게 달라붙는 강철의 폭탄을 발사한다. 공격은 반드시 명중한다.

name: Stone Edge
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move.
effect_entry_ko: 뾰족한 바위를 상대에게 꿰찔러서 공격한다. 급소에 맞기 쉽다.

name: Captivate
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Special Attack by two stages. If the user and target are the same gender, or either is genderless, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 수컷은 암컷을 암컷은 수컷을 유혹하여 상대의 특수공격을 크게 떨어뜨린다.

name: Stealth Rock
effect_entry: Spreads sharp rocks around the opposing field, damaging any Pokémon that enters the field for 1/8 its max HP. This damage is affected by the entering Pokémon's susceptibility to rock moves. rapid spin removes this effect from its user's side of the field.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 주위에 무수한 바위를 띄워 교체해서 나온 상대 포켓몬에게 데미지를 준다.

name: Grass Knot
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power increases with the target's weight in kilograms, to a maximum of 120. Target's weight | Power --------------- | ----: Up to 10kg   |  20 Up to 25kg   |  40 Up to 50kg   |  60 Up to 100kg   |  80 Up to 200kg   |  100 Above 200kg   |  120
effect_entry_ko: 풀을 휘감아서 상대를 쓰러뜨린다. 상대가 무거울수록 위력이 올라간다.

name: Chatter
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has either a 1%, 11%, or 31% chance to confuse the target, based on the volume of the recording made for this move; louder recordings increase the chance of confusion. If the user is not a chatot, this move will not cause confusion. This move cannot be copied by mimic, mirror move, or sketch, nor selected by assist, metronome, or sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 기억한 말로 음파를 일으켜서 공격한다. 상대를 혼란시킨다.

name: Judgment
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the user is holding a plate or a drive, this move's type is the type corresponding to that item. Note: This effect is technically shared by both techno blast and judgment; however, Techno Blast is only affected by drives, and Judgment is only affected by plates.
effect_entry_ko: 무수한 광탄을 상대에게 방출한다. 자신이 가지고 있는 플레이트에 따라 타입이 바뀐다.

name: Bug Bite
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target is holding a berry, this move has double power, and the user takes the berry and uses it immediately. If the target is holding a jaboca berry or rowap berry, the berry is still removed, but has no effect. If this move is super effective and the target is holding a berry that can reduce this move's damage, it will do so, and will not be stolen.
effect_entry_ko: 물어서 공격한다. 상대가 나무열매를 지니고 있을 때 먹어서 나무열매의 효과를 받을 수 있다.

name: Charge Beam
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 70% chance to raise the user's Special Attack by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 전격의 다발을 상대에게 발사한다. 전기를 모아서 자신의 특수공격을 올릴 때가 있다.

name: Wood Hammer
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User takes 1/3 the damage it inflicts in recoil.
effect_entry_ko: 단단한 몸통을 상대에게 부딪쳐서 공격한다. 자신도 상당한 데미지를 입는다.

name: Aqua Jet
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 눈에 보이지 않는 굉장한 속도로 상대에게 돌진한다. 반드시 선제공격할 수 있다.

name: Attack Order
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move.
effect_entry_ko: 부하를 불러내어 상대를 향해서 공격시킨다. 급소에 맞기 쉽다.

name: Defend Order
effect_entry: Raises the user's Defense and Special Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 부하를 불러내어 자신의 몸을 뒤덮게 한다. 방어와 특수방어를 올릴 수 있다.

name: Heal Order
effect_entry: Heals the user for half its max HP.
effect_entry_ko: 부하를 불러내어 상처를 회복한다. 최대 HP의 절반만큼 자신의 HP를 회복한다.

name: Head Smash
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User takes 1/2 the damage it inflicts in recoil.
effect_entry_ko: 목숨을 걸고 혼신의 힘으로 상대에게 박치기를 한다. 자신도 굉장한 데미지를 입는다.

name: Double Hit
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits twice in one turn.
effect_entry_ko: 꼬리 등을 써서 상대를 때려 공격한다. 2회 연속으로 데미지를 준다.

name: Roar of Time
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User loses its next turn to "recharge", and cannot attack or switch out during that turn.
effect_entry_ko: 시간이 뒤틀릴 정도의 힘을 사용해서 상대를 공격한다. 다음 턴은 움직일 수 없다.

name: Spacial Rend
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move.
effect_entry_ko: 주위의 공간과 더불어 상대를 찢어서 데미지를 준다. 급소에 맞기 쉽다.

name: Lunar Dance
effect_entry: User faints. Its replacement's HP and PP are fully restored, and any major status effect is removed.
effect_entry_ko: 자신은 기절하지만 교대하여 나오는 포켓몬의 모든 상태를 회복한다.

name: Crush Grip
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power directly relates to the target's relative remaining HP, given by `1 + 120 * current HP / max HP`, to a maximum of 121.
effect_entry_ko: 굉장한 힘으로 상대를 묵사발로 만든다. 상대의 HP가 남아 있을수록 위력이 올라간다.

name: Magma Storm
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. For the next 2–5 turns, the target cannot leave the field and is damaged for 1/16 its max HP at the end of each turn. The user continues to use other moves during this time. If the user leaves the field, this effect ends. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use. rapid spin cancels this effect.
effect_entry_ko: 세차게 타오르는 불꽃 속에 4-5턴 동안 상대를 가두어 공격한다.

name: Dark Void
effect_entry: Puts the target to sleep.
effect_entry_ko: 암흑의 세계로 끌고 가서 떨어뜨려 상대를 잠듦 상태로 만든다.

name: Seed Flare
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 40% chance to lower the target's Special Defense by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 몸속에서 충격파를 발생시킨다. 상대의 특수방어를 크게 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Ominous Wind
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to raise all of the user's stats one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 소름이 끼칠 만한 돌풍으로 상대를 공격한다. 자신의 모든 능력이 올라갈 때가 있다.

name: Shadow Force
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User vanishes for one turn, becoming immune to attack, and hits on the second turn. This move ignores the effects of detect and protect. This move cannot be selected by sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 1턴째에 모습을 감춰 2턴째에 상대를 공격한다. 방어하고 있어도 공격은 맞는다.

name: Hone Claws
effect_entry: Raises the user's Attack and accuracy by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 손톱을 갈아 날카롭게 한다. 자신의 공격과 명중률을 올린다.

name: Wide Guard
effect_entry: Moves with multiple targets will not hit friendly Pokémon for the remainder of this turn. If the user is last to act this turn, this move will fail. This move cannot be selected by assist or metronome.
effect_entry_ko: 같은 편 전원에게 향하는 공격을 1턴 동안 막는다.

name: Guard Split
effect_entry: Averages the user's unmodified Defense with the target's unmodified Defense; the value becomes the unmodified Defense for both Pokémon. Unmodified Special Defense is averaged the same way.
effect_entry_ko: 초능력으로 자신과 상대의 방어와 특수방어를 더해서 반으로 나눈다.

name: Power Split
effect_entry: Averages the user's unmodified Attack with the target's unmodified Attack; the value becomes the unmodified Attack for both Pokémon. Unmodified Special Attack is averaged the same way. This effect applies before any other persistent changes to unmodified Attack or Special Attack, such as flower gift during sunny day.
effect_entry_ko: 초능력으로 자신과 상대의 공격과 특수공격을 더해서 반으로 나눈다.

name: Wonder Room
effect_entry: For five turns (including this one), every Pokémon's Defense and Special Defense are swapped.
effect_entry_ko: 이상한 공간을 만든다. 5턴 동안 모든 포켓몬의 방어와 특수방어가 바뀐다.

name: Psyshock
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Damage calculation always uses the target's Defense, regardless of this move's damage class.
effect_entry_ko: 이상한 염력파를 실체화하여 상대를 공격한다. 물리적인 데미지를 준다.

name: Venoshock
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target is poisoned, this move has double power.
effect_entry_ko: 특수한 독액을 끼얹는다. 독 상태의 상대에게는 위력이 2배가 된다.

name: Autotomize
effect_entry: Raises the user's Speed by two stages. Halves the user's weight; this effect does not stack.
effect_entry_ko: 몸의 쓸모없는 부분을 깎는다. 자신의 스피드를 크게 올리고 체중도 가벼워진다.

name: Rage Powder
effect_entry: Until the end of this turn, any moves that opposing Pokémon target solely at the user's ally will instead target the user. If both Pokémon on the same side of the field use this move on the same turn, the Pokémon that uses it last will become the target. This effect takes priority over lightning rod and storm drain. If the user's ally switches out, opposing Pokémon may still hit it with pursuit. This move cannot be selected by assist or metronome.
effect_entry_ko: 안절부절못하게 하는 가루를 자신에게 뿌려서 주의를 끈다. 상대의 공격은 모두 자신에게 향한다.

name: Telekinesis
effect_entry: For three turns (including this one), moves used against the target have 100% accuracy, but the target is immune to ground damage. Accuracy of one-hit KO moves is exempt from this effect. This effect is removed by gravity. If Gravity is already in effect, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 초능력으로 상대를 띄운다. 3턴 동안 공격이 상대에게 맞기 쉬워진다.

name: Magic Room
effect_entry: For five turns (including this one), passive effects of held items are ignored, and Pokémon will not use their held items.
effect_entry_ko: 이상한 공간을 만든다. 5턴 동안 모든 포켓몬의 도구의 효과가 사라진다.

name: Smack Down
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Removes the target's immunity to ground-type damage. This effect removes any existing Ground immunity due to levitate, magnet rise, or telekinesis, and causes the target's flying type to be ignored when it takes Ground damage. If the target isn't immune to Ground damage, this move will fail. This move can hit Pokémon under the effect of bounce, fly, or sky drop, and ends the effect of Bounce or Fly.
effect_entry_ko: 돌이나 구슬을 던져서 날고 있는 상대를 공격한다. 맞은 상대는 땅에 떨어진다.

name: Storm Throw
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Always scores a critical hit.
effect_entry_ko: 강렬한 일격을 상대에게 날린다. 공격은 반드시 급소에 맞는다.

name: Flame Burst
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If this move successfully hits the target, any Pokémon adjacent to the target are damaged for 1/16 their max HP.
effect_entry_ko: 맞으면 튀는 불꽃으로 상대를 공격한다. 튕긴 불꽃은 옆의 상대에게도 쏟아진다.

name: Sludge Wave
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to poison the target.
effect_entry_ko: 오물 파도로 자신의 주위에 있는 포켓몬을 공격한다. 독 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Quiver Dance
effect_entry: Raises the user's Special Attack, Special Defense, and Speed by one stage each.
effect_entry_ko: 신비롭고 아름다운 춤을 경쾌하게 춘다. 자신의 특수공격과 특수방어와 스피드를 올린다.

name: Heavy Slam
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. The greater the user's weight compared to the target's, the higher power this move has, to a maximum of 120. User's weight          | Power -------------------------------- | ----: Up to 2× the target's weight   |  40 Up to 3× the target's weight   |  60 Up to 4× the target's weight   |  80 Up to 5× the target's weight   |  100 More than 5× the target's weight |  120
effect_entry_ko: 무거운 몸으로 상대에게 부딪쳐 공격한다. 자신이 상대보다 무거울수록 위력이 올라간다.

name: Synchronoise
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Only Pokémon that share a type with the user will take damage from this move.
effect_entry_ko: 이상한 전파로 주위에 있는 자신과 같은 타입의 포켓몬에게 데미지를 준다.

name: Electro Ball
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. The greater the user's Speed compared to the target's, the higher power this move has, to a maximum of 150. User's Speed           | Power -------------------------------- | ----: Up to 2× the target's Speed   |  60 Up to 3× the target's Speed   |  80 Up to 4× the target's Speed   |  120 More than 4× the target's Speed |  150
effect_entry_ko: 전기 덩어리를 상대에게 부딪쳐서 공격한다. 상대보다 스피드가 빠를수록 위력이 올라간다.

name: Soak
effect_entry: Changes the target to pure water-type until it leaves the field. If the target has multitype, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 많은 물을 끼얹어서 상대를 물타입으로 바꾼다.

name: Flame Charge
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Raises the user's Speed by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 불꽃을 둘러 상대를 공격한다. 힘을 모아서 자신의 스피드를 올린다.

name: Coil
effect_entry: Raises the user's Attack, Defense, and accuracy by one stage each.
effect_entry_ko: 똬리를 틀어서 집중한다. 자신의 공격과 방어와 명중률을 올린다.

name: Low Sweep
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Speed by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 재빠른 움직임으로 상대의 다리를 노려 공격한다. 상대의 스피드를 떨어뜨린다.

name: Acid Spray
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Lowers the target's Special Defense by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 상대를 녹이는 액체를 토해내서 공격한다. 상대의 특수방어를 크게 떨어뜨린다.

name: Foul Play
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Damage is calculated using the target's attacking stat rather than the user's.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 힘을 이용한다. 싸우고 있는 상대의 공격이 높을수록 데미지가 올라간다.

name: Simple Beam
effect_entry: Changes the target's ability to simple.
effect_entry_ko: 수수께끼의 염력파를 상대에게 보낸다. 염력파를 받은 상대는 특성이 단순으로 바뀐다.

name: Entrainment
effect_entry: Changes the target's ability to match the user's. This effect ends when the target leaves battle.
effect_entry_ko: 이상한 리듬으로 춤춘다. 움직임을 흉내 내게 해서 자신과 상대의 특성을 똑같게 만든다.

name: After You
effect_entry: The target will act next this turn, regardless of Speed or move priority. If the target has already acted this turn, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 행동을 도와서 자신이 행동한 뒤에 바로 움직일 수 있도록 한다.

name: Round
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If round has already been used this turn, this move's power is doubled. After this move is used, any other Pokémon using it this turn will immediately do so (in the order they would otherwise act), regardless of Speed or priority. Pokémon using other moves will then continue to act as usual.
effect_entry_ko: 노래로 상대를 공격한다. 함께 돌림노래를 하면 계속해서 쓸 수 있고 위력도 올라간다.

name: Echoed Voice
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If any friendly Pokémon used this move earlier this turn or on the previous turn, that use's power is added to this move's power, to a maximum of 200.
effect_entry_ko: 울리는 목소리로 상대를 공격한다. 매 턴 누군가 기술을 계속해서 쓰면 위력이 올라간다.

name: Chip Away
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Damage calculation ignores the target's stat modifiers, including evasion.
effect_entry_ko: 틈을 보며 착실하게 공격한다. 상대의 능력 변화에 관계없이 데미지를 준다.

name: Clear Smog
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. All of the target's stat modifiers are reset to zero.
effect_entry_ko: 특수한 진흙 덩어리를 상대에게 내던져서 공격한다. 능력 변화를 원래대로 돌린다.

name: Stored Power
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Power is increased by 100% its original value for every stage any of the user's stats have been raised. Accuracy, evasion, and lowered stats do not affect this move's power. For a Pokémon with all five stats modified to +6, this move's power is 31×.
effect_entry_ko: 축적된 파워로 상대를 공격한다. 자신의 능력이 올라가 있는 만큼 위력이 오른다.

name: Quick Guard
effect_entry: Moves with priority greater than 0 will not hit friendly Pokémon for the remainder of this turn. If the user is last to act this turn, this move will fail. This move cannot be selected by assist or metronome.
effect_entry_ko: 자신과 같은 편을 상대의 선제공격으로부터 지킨다.

name: Ally Switch
effect_entry: User switches position on the field with the friendly Pokémon opposite it. If the user is in the middle position in a triple battle, or there are no other friendly Pokémon, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 이상한 힘으로 순간이동하여 자신과 같은 편이 있는 장소를 바꾼다.

name: Scald
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to burn the target.
effect_entry_ko: 뜨겁게 끓어오르는 물을 상대에게 발사해서 공격한다. 화상 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Shell Smash
effect_entry: Raises the user's Attack, Special Attack, and Speed by two stages each. Lowers the user's Defense and Special Defense by one stage each.
effect_entry_ko: 껍질을 깨서 자신의 방어와 특수방어를 떨어뜨리지만 공격과 특수공격, 스피드를 크게 올린다.

name: Heal Pulse
effect_entry: Heals the target for half its max HP.
effect_entry_ko: 치유파동을 날려서 최대 HP의 절반만큼 상대의 HP를 회복한다.

name: Hex
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target has a major status ailment, this move has double power.
effect_entry_ko: 엎친 데 덮친 격으로 공격한다. 상태 이상인 상대에게 큰 데미지를 준다.

name: Sky Drop
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User carries the target high into the air for one turn, during which no moves will hit either Pokémon and neither can act. On the following turn, the user drops the target, inflicting damage and ending the effect. If the target is flying-type, this move will function as normal but inflict no damage. gust, hurricane, sky uppercut, smack down, thunder, twister, and whirlwind can hit both the user and the target during this effect. gust and twister will additionally have double power. The damage from hail and sandstorm still applies during this effect. Either Pokémon may be hit during this effect if also under the effect of lock on, mind reader, or no guard. This move cannot be used while gravity is in effect. This move cannot be selected by sleep talk. *Bug*: If gravity is used during a double or triple battle while this move is in effect, this move is not correctly canceled on the target, and it remains high in the air indefinitely. As this move prevents the target from acting, the only way to subsequently remove it from the field is to faint it.
effect_entry_ko: 1턴째에 상대를 하늘로 끌고 가서 2턴째에 떨어뜨려 공격한다. 끌려간 상대는 움직일 수 없다.

name: Shift Gear
effect_entry: Raises the user's Attack by one stage and its Speed by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 톱니바퀴를 돌려서 자신의 공격을 올리는 것뿐만 아니라 스피드도 크게 올린다.

name: Circle Throw
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage, then switches the target out for another of its trainer's Pokémon, selected at random. If the target is under the effect of ingrain or suction cups, or it has a substitute, or its Trainer has no more usable Pokémon, it will not be switched out. If the target is a wild Pokémon, the battle ends instead.
effect_entry_ko: 상대를 내던져서 교대할 포켓몬을 끌어낸다. 야생의 경우에는 배틀이 끝난다.

name: Incinerate
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the target is holding a berry, it's destroyed and cannot be used in response to this move.
effect_entry_ko: 불꽃으로 상대를 공격한다. 상대가 나무열매 등을 지니고 있을 때 불태워서 쓸 수 없게 만든다.

name: Quash
effect_entry: Forces the target to act last this turn, regardless of Speed or move priority. If the target has already acted this turn, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 상대를 억눌러서 행동의 순서를 마지막으로 만든다.

name: Acrobatics
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the user has no held item, this move has double power.
effect_entry_ko: 경쾌하게 상대를 공격한다. 자신이 도구를 지니고 있지 않을 때 큰 데미지를 준다.

name: Reflect Type
effect_entry: User's type changes to match the target's.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 타입을 반사해서 자신도 똑같은 타입이 된다.

name: Retaliate
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If a friendly Pokémon fainted on the previous turn, this move has double power.
effect_entry_ko: 쓰러진 같은 편의 원수를 갚는다. 앞 턴에서 같은 편이 쓰러졌다면 위력이 올라간다.

name: Final Gambit
effect_entry: Inflicts damage equal to the user's remaining HP. User faints.
effect_entry_ko: 목숨을 걸고 상대를 공격한다. 자신은 기절하게 되지만 상대에게 HP만큼의 데미지를 준다.

name: Bestow
effect_entry: Transfers the user's held item to the target. If the user has no held item, or the target already has a held item, this move will fail.
effect_entry_ko: 상대가 도구를 지니고 있지 않을 때 자신이 지니고 있는 도구를 상대에게 건넨다.

name: Inferno
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 100% chance to burn the target.
effect_entry_ko: 격렬한 불꽃으로 상대를 둘러싸 공격한다. 화상 상태로 만든다.

name: Water Pledge
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If a friendly Pokémon used grass pledge earlier this turn, all opposing Pokémon have halved Speed for four turns (including this one).
effect_entry_ko: 물기둥으로 공격한다. 불꽃과 조합하면 위력이 올라가고 하늘에 무지개가 걸린다.

name: Fire Pledge
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If a friendly Pokémon used water pledge earlier this turn, moves used by any friendly Pokémon have doubled effect chance for four turns (including this one).
effect_entry_ko: 불꽃기둥으로 공격한다. 풀과 조합하면 위력이 올라가고 주위가 불바다가 된다.

name: Grass Pledge
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If a friendly Pokémon used fire pledge earlier this turn, all opposing Pokémon will take 1/8 their max HP in damage at the end of every turn for four turns (including this one).
effect_entry_ko: 풀기둥으로 공격한다. 물과 조합하면 위력이 올라가고 주변이 습지초원이 된다.

name: Volt Switch
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage, then the user immediately switches out, and the trainer selects a replacement Pokémon from the party. If the target faints from this attack, the user's trainer selects the new Pokémon to send out first. If the user is the last Pokémon in its party that can battle, it will not switch out. The user may be hit by pursuit when it switches out, if it has been targeted and pursuit has not yet been used. This move may be used even if the user is under the effect of ingrain. ingrain's effect will end.
effect_entry_ko: 공격한 뒤 굉장한 스피드로 돌아와서 교대 포켓몬과 교체한다.

name: Struggle Bug
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 100% chance to lower the target's Special Attack by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 저항해서 상대를 공격한다. 상대의 특수공격을 떨어뜨린다.

name: Bulldoze
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 100% chance to lower the target's Speed by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 땅을 힘껏 밟아 자신의 주위에 있는 포켓몬을 공격한다. 상대의 스피드를 떨어뜨린다.

name: Frost Breath
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Always scores a critical hit.
effect_entry_ko: 차가운 숨결을 상대에게 내뿜어 공격한다. 반드시 급소에 맞는다.

name: Dragon Tail
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage, then switches the target out for another of its trainer's Pokémon, selected at random. If the target is under the effect of ingrain or suction cups, or it has a substitute, or its Trainer has no more usable Pokémon, it will not be switched out. If the target is a wild Pokémon, the battle ends instead.
effect_entry_ko: 상대를 튕겨내서 교대할 포켓몬을 끌어낸다. 야생의 경우에는 배틀이 끝난다.

name: Work Up
effect_entry: Raises the user's Attack and Special Attack by one stage each.
effect_entry_ko: 스스로 분발해서 공격과 특수공격을 올린다.

name: Electroweb
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Speed by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 전기 네트로 상대를 붙잡아서 공격한다. 상대의 스피드를 떨어뜨린다.

name: Wild Charge
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User takes 1/4 the damage it inflicts in recoil.
effect_entry_ko: 전기를 두르고 상대에게 부딪쳐 공격한다. 자신도 조금 데미지를 입는다.

name: Drill Run
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User's critical hit rate is one level higher when using this move.
effect_entry_ko: 드릴처럼 몸을 회전시켜서 상대에게 몸통박치기한다. 급소에 맞기 쉽다.

name: Dual Chop
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits twice in one turn.
effect_entry_ko: 몸의 단단한 부분으로 상대를 때려 공격한다. 2회 연속으로 데미지를 준다.

name: Heart Stamp
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 귀여운 모습으로 방심시켜서 강렬한 일격을 날린다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: Horn Leech
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Drains half the damage inflicted to heal the user.
effect_entry_ko: 뿔을 꿰찔러서 상대의 양분을 흡수한다. 입힌 데미지의 절반에 해당하는 HP를 회복할 수 있다.

name: Sacred Sword
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Damage calculation ignores the target's stat modifiers, including evasion.
effect_entry_ko: 긴 뿔로 베어 공격한다. 상대의 능력 변화에 관계없이 데미지를 준다.

name: Razor Shell
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 50% chance to lower the target's Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 날카로운 조개껍질로 베어 공격한다. 상대의 방어를 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Heat Crash
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. The greater the user's weight compared to the target's, the higher power this move has, to a maximum of 120. User's weight          | Power -------------------------------- | ----: Up to 2× the target's weight   |  40 Up to 3× the target's weight   |  60 Up to 4× the target's weight   |  80 Up to 5× the target's weight   |  100 More than 5× the target's weight |  120
effect_entry_ko: 불타는 몸으로 상대에게 부딪쳐서 공격한다. 자신이 상대보다 무거울수록 위력이 올라간다.

name: Leaf Tornado
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 50% chance to lower the target's accuracy by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 날카로운 잎사귀로 상대를 둘러싸서 공격한다. 명중률을 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Steamroller
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to make the target flinch. Power is doubled against Pokémon that have used minimize since entering the field.
effect_entry_ko: 둥글게 뭉친 몸을 회전하여 상대를 뭉개 버린다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: Cotton Guard
effect_entry: Raises the user's Defense by three stages.
effect_entry_ko: 푹신푹신한 솜털로 자신의 몸을 둘러싸서 지킨다. 방어를 매우 크게 올린다.

name: Night Daze
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 40% chance to lower the target's accuracy by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 암흑의 충격파를 날려서 상대를 공격한다. 명중률을 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Psystrike
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Damage calculation always uses the target's Defense, regardless of this move's damage class.
effect_entry_ko: 이상한 염력파를 실체화하여 상대를 공격한다. 물리적인 데미지를 준다.

name: Tail Slap
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits 2–5 times in one turn. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use.
effect_entry_ko: 단단한 꼬리로 상대를 때려서 공격한다. 2-5회 동안 연속으로 쓴다.

name: Hurricane
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to confuse the target. This move can hit Pokémon under the effect of bounce, fly, or sky drop. During rain dance, this move has 100% accuracy. During sunny day, this move has 50% accuracy.
effect_entry_ko: 강렬한 바람으로 상대를 둘러싸서 공격한다. 상대를 혼란시킬 때가 있다.

name: Head Charge
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User takes 1/4 the damage it inflicts in recoil.
effect_entry_ko: 굉장한 아프로 머리로 상대에게 돌진하여 공격한다. 자신도 조금 데미지를 입는다.

name: Gear Grind
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits twice in one turn.
effect_entry_ko: 강철의 기어를 상대에게 던져서 공격한다. 2회 연속으로 데미지를 준다.

name: Searing Shot
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to burn the target.
effect_entry_ko: 새빨간 불꽃으로 자신의 주위에 있는 포켓몬을 공격한다. 화상 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Techno Blast
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If the user is holding a plate or a drive, this move's type is the type corresponding to that item. Note: This effect is technically shared by both techno blast and judgment; however, Techno Blast is only affected by drives, and Judgment is only affected by plates.
effect_entry_ko: 광탄을 상대에게 방출한다. 자신이 지니고 있는 카세트에 의해 타입이 바뀐다.

name: Relic Song
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to put the target to sleep. If the user is a meloetta, it will toggle between Aria and Pirouette Forme.
effect_entry_ko: 옛노래를 상대에게 들려주고 마음에 호소하여 공격한다. 잠듦 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Secret Sword
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Damage calculation always uses the target's Defense, regardless of this move's damage class.
effect_entry_ko: 긴 뿔로 베어 공격한다. 뿔이 머금은 이상한 힘은 물리적인 데미지를 준다.

name: Glaciate
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Lowers the target's Speed by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 차가운 냉기를 상대에게 내뿜어 공격한다. 상대의 스피드를 떨어뜨린다.

name: Bolt Strike
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 20% chance to paralyze the target.
effect_entry_ko: 방대한 전기를 몸에 둘러 상대에게 돌진해서 공격한다. 마비 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Blue Flare
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 20% chance to burn the target.
effect_entry_ko: 아름다우면서도 격렬한 푸른불꽃으로 상대를 둘러싸서 공격한다. 화상 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Fiery Dance
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 50% chance to raise the user's Special Attack by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 불꽃을 둘러 날개를 쳐서 공격한다. 자신의 특수공격이 오를 때가 있다.

name: Freeze Shock
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to paralyze the target. User charges for one turn before attacking.
effect_entry_ko: 전기를 두른 얼음 덩어리로 2턴째에 상대를 내리친다. 마비 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Ice Burn
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to burn the target. User charges for one turn before attacking.
effect_entry_ko: 모든 것을 얼려버리는 격렬한 냉기로 2턴째에 상대를 둘러싼다. 화상 상태로 만들 때가 있다.

name: Snarl
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 100% chance to lower the target's Special Attack by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 호되게 호통을 쳐서 상대의 특수공격을 떨어뜨린다.

name: Icicle Crash
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to make the target flinch.
effect_entry_ko: 큰 고드름을 격렬하게 부딪쳐서 공격한다. 상대를 풀죽게 만들 때가 있다.

name: V-create
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Lowers the user's Defense, Special Defense, and Speed by one stage each.
effect_entry_ko: 작열하는 불꽃을 이마에서 발생시켜 이판사판으로 몸통박치기한다. 방어, 특수방어, 스피드가 떨어진다.

name: Fusion Flare
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If a friendly Pokémon used fusion bolt earlier this turn, this move has double power.
effect_entry_ko: 거대한 불꽃을 내리친다. 거대한 천둥의 영향을 받아 기술의 위력이 올라간다.

name: Fusion Bolt
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. If a friendly Pokémon used fusion flare earlier this turn, this move has double power.
effect_entry_ko: 거대한 천둥을 내리친다. 거대한 불꽃의 영향을 받아 기술의 위력이 올라간다.

name: Flying Press
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. For the purposes of type effectiveness, this move is both fighting- and flying-type: its final effectiveness is determined by multiplying the effectiveness of each type against each of the target's types. For all other purposes, this move is pure Fighting-type. If this move's type is changed, its Fighting typing is overwritten, and its secondary type remains Flying. If the target has used minimize since entering battle, this move has double power and will never miss.
effect_entry_ko: 공중에서 상대에게 다이브한다. 이 기술은 격투타입임과 동시에 비행타입이기도 하다.

name: Mat Block
effect_entry: Protects all friendly Pokémon from damaging moves. Only works on the first turn after the user is sent out.
effect_entry_ko: 뒤집어 세운 마룻바닥을 방패로 하여 자신과 같은 편으로 향하는 기술 데미지를 막는다. 변화 기술은 막을 수 없다.

name: Belch
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Can only be used if the user has eaten a berry since the beginning of the battle. After the user eats a berry, it may use this move any number of times until the end of the battle, even if it switches out. Eating a held berry, eating a berry via bug bite or pluck, or being the target of a Flung berry will enable this move. Feeding a Pokémon a berry from the bag or using natural gift will not. If the trainer chooses this move when it cannot be used, the choice is rejected outright and the trainer must choose another move.
effect_entry_ko: 상대를 향해 트림을 하여 데미지를 준다. 나무열매를 먹지 않으면 쓸 수 없다.

name: Rototiller
effect_entry: Raises the Attack and Special Attack of all grass Pokémon in battle.
effect_entry_ko: 땅을 일구어 초목이 자라기 쉽게 한다. 풀타입의 공격과 특수공격이 오른다.

name: Sticky Web
effect_entry: Shoots a web over the opponents' side of the field, which lowers the Speed of any opposing Pokémon that enters the field by one stage. Pokémon in the air, such as flying-types and those with levitate, are unaffected. rapid spin removes Sticky Web from the user's side of the field; defog removes it from both sides.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 주위에 끈적끈적한 네트를 둘러 펼쳐 교체되어 나온 상대의 스피드를 떨어뜨린다.

name: Fell Stinger
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Raises the user's Attack by two stages if it KOs the target.
effect_entry_ko: 이 기술을 사용하여 상대를 쓰러뜨리면 공격이 크게 오른다.

name: Phantom Force
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User vanishes for one turn, becoming immune to attack, and hits on the second turn. This move ignores the effects of detect and protect. This move cannot be selected by sleep talk.
effect_entry_ko: 1턴째에 어디론가 사라져서 2턴째에 상대를 공격한다. 기술 방어를 무시하고 공격할 수 있다.

name: Trick-or-Treat
effect_entry: Adds ghost to the target's types.
effect_entry_ko: 상대를 핼러윈으로 초대한다. 상대 타입에 고스트타입이 추가된다.

name: Noble Roar
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Attack and Special Attack by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 우렁차게 부르짖어서 상대를 위협하여 상대의 공격과 특수공격을 떨어뜨린다.

name: Ion Deluge
effect_entry: Changes all Pokémon's normal moves to electric moves for the rest of the turn.
effect_entry_ko: 전기를 띤 입자를 확산시켜 노말타입 기술을 전기타입으로 바꿔버린다.

name: Parabolic Charge
effect_entry: Heals the user for half the total damage dealt to all targets.
effect_entry_ko: 주위에 있는 모든 포켓몬에게 데미지를 준다. 준 데미지의 절반을 자신이 회복한다.

name: Forest's Curse
effect_entry: Adds grass to the target's types.
effect_entry_ko: 상대에게 숲의 저주를 건다. 저주에 걸린 상대는 타입에 풀타입이 추가된다.

name: Petal Blizzard
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 세찬 꽃보라를 일으켜서 주위에 있는 포켓몬을 공격하여 데미지를 준다.

name: Freeze-Dry
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. This move is super-effective against the water type. The target's other type will affect damage as usual. If this move's type is changed, it remains super-effective against Water regardless of its type.
effect_entry_ko: 상대를 급격히 차갑게 하여 얼음 상태로 만들 때가 있다. 물타입 포켓몬에게도 효과가 굉장해진다.

name: Disarming Voice
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Ignores accuracy and evasion.
effect_entry_ko: 매혹적인 울음소리를 내어 상대에게 정신적 데미지를 준다. 공격은 반드시 명중한다.

name: Parting Shot
effect_entry: Lowers all targets' Attack and Special Attack by one stage. Makes the user switch out.
effect_entry_ko: 막말을 내뱉어 상대를 위협하여 공격과 특수공격을 떨어뜨린 후 교대 포켓몬과 교체한다.

name: Topsy-Turvy
effect_entry: Inverts the target's stat modifiers.
effect_entry_ko: 상대에게 걸려 있는 모든 능력 변화를 뒤집어서 반대로 만든다.

name: Draining Kiss
effect_entry: Deals regular damage. Drains 75% of the damage inflicted to heal the user.
effect_entry_ko: 키스로 상대로부터 HP를 흡수한다. 준 데미지의 반 이상 HP를 회복한다.

name: Crafty Shield
effect_entry: Protects all friendly Pokémon from non-damaging moves for the rest of the turn. Unlike other blocking moves, this move may be used consecutively without its chance of success falling.
effect_entry_ko: 이상한 힘을 사용하여 같은 편을 공격하는 변화 기술을 막는다. 데미지 기술은 받는다.

name: Flower Shield
effect_entry: Raises the Defense of all grass Pokémon in battle.
effect_entry_ko: 이상한 힘을 사용하여 배틀에 나와있는 모든 풀타입 포켓몬의 방어를 올린다.

name: Grassy Terrain
effect_entry: For five turns, heals all Pokémon on the ground for 1/16 their max HP each turn and strengthens their grass moves to 1.5× their power. Changes nature power to energy ball.
effect_entry_ko: 5턴 동안 발밑을 그래스필드로 만든다. 땅에 있는 포켓몬은 매 턴 회복한다.

name: Misty Terrain
effect_entry: For five turns, protects all Pokémon on the ground from major status ailments and confusion and weakens dragon moves used against them to 0.5× their power. Changes nature power to moonblast.
effect_entry_ko: 5턴 동안 발밑을 미스트필드로 만든다. 땅에 있으면 상태 이상이 되지 않는다.

name: Electrify
effect_entry: Changes the target's move's type to electric if it hasn't moved yet this turn.
effect_entry_ko: 상대가 기술을 쓰기 전에 송전하면 그 턴에 상대가 사용하는 기술은 전기타입이 된다.

name: Play Rough
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 10% chance to lower the target's Attack by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 상대에게 치근거리며 공격한다. 상대의 공격을 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Fairy Wind
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 요정의 바람을 일으켜 상대에게 몰아쳐서 공격한다.

name: Moonblast
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to lower the target's Special Attack by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 달의 파워를 빌려서 상대를 공격한다. 상대의 특수공격을 떨어뜨릴 때가 있다.

name: Boomburst
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 무시무시한 폭음의 파괴력으로 주위에 있는 포켓몬을 공격한다.

name: Fairy Lock
effect_entry: Prevents all Pokémon from fleeing or switching out during the next turn.
effect_entry_ko: 록을 걸어 다음 턴의 모든 포켓몬을 도망가지 못하게 한다.

name: King's Shield
effect_entry: Blocks damaging attacks and lowers attacking Pokémon's Attack by two stages on contact. Switches Aegislash to Shield Forme.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 공격을 막음과 동시에 방어 태세를 갖춘다. 접촉한 상대의 공격을 크게 떨어뜨린다.

name: Play Nice
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Attack by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 상대와 친해져서 싸울 마음을 잃게 하여 상대의 공격을 떨어뜨린다.

name: Confide
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Special Attack by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 비밀 이야기를 하면서 상대의 집중력을 잃게 하여 상대의 특수공격을 떨어뜨린다.

name: Diamond Storm
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 50% chance to raise the user's Defense by two stages for each target hit.
effect_entry_ko: 다이아 폭풍을 일으켜 데미지를 준다. 자신의 방어를 올릴 때가 있다.

name: Steam Eruption
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 30% chance to burn the target.
effect_entry_ko: 상대에게 굉장히 뜨거운 증기를 뿜는다. 상대는 화상을 입기도 한다.

name: Hyperspace Hole
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Bypasses and removes any protection effect on the target.
effect_entry_ko: 다른차원홀로 갑자기 상대 바로 옆에 나타나 공격한다. 방어나 판별도 무시할 수 있다.

name: Water Shuriken
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Hits 2–5 times.
effect_entry_ko: 점액으로 만든 수리검을 2-5회 동안 연속으로 던진다. 반드시 선제공격할 수 있다.

name: Mystical Fire
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 100% chance to lower the target's Special Attack by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 입에서 내뱉는 아주 뜨거운 불꽃으로 공격한다. 상대의 특수공격을 떨어뜨린다.

name: Spiky Shield
effect_entry: Blocks damaging attacks and damages attacking Pokémon for 1/8 their max HP.
effect_entry_ko: 상대의 공격을 막음과 동시에 접촉한 상대의 체력을 떨어뜨린다.

name: Aromatic Mist
effect_entry: Raises a selected ally's Special Defense by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 신비한 아로마 향으로 같은 편의 특수방어를 올린다.

name: Eerie Impulse
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Special Attack by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 몸에서 괴전파를 내어 상대에게 쏨으로써 특수공격을 크게 떨어뜨린다.

name: Venom Drench
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Attack, Special Attack, and Speed by one stage if it is poisoned.
effect_entry_ko: 특수한 독액을 끼얹는다. 독 상태인 상대는 공격, 특수공격, 스피드가 떨어진다.

name: Powder
effect_entry: Explodes if the target uses a fire move this turn, damaging it for 1/4 its max HP and preventing the move.
effect_entry_ko: 분진을 뒤집어쓴 상대가 불꽃 기술을 쓰면 폭발하여 데미지를 준다.

name: Geomancy
effect_entry: Takes one turn to charge, then raises the user's Special Attack, Special Defense, and Speed by two stages.
effect_entry_ko: 1턴째에 에너지를 흡수하여 2턴째에 특수공격, 특수방어, 스피드를 크게 올린다.

name: Magnetic Flux
effect_entry: Raises the Defense and Special Defense of all friendly Pokémon with plus or minus by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 자기장 조작으로 인해 특성 플러스와 마이너스의 방어, 특수방어가 오른다.

name: Happy Hour
effect_entry: Doubles prize money. Stacks with a held item. Only works once per battle.
effect_entry_ko: 해피타임 기술을 쓰면 배틀 후에 받을 수 있는 돈이 배가 된다.

name: Electric Terrain
effect_entry: For five turns, prevents all Pokémon on the ground from sleeping and strengthens their electric moves to 1.5× their power. Changes nature power to thunderbolt.
effect_entry_ko: 5턴 동안 발밑을 일렉트릭필드로 만든다. 땅에 있는 포켓몬은 잠들지 않게 된다.

name: Dazzling Gleam
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 강력한 빛을 내어 상대에게 데미지를 준다.

name: Celebrate
effect_entry: Does nothing.
effect_entry_ko: 포켓몬이 매우 행복한 당신을 축하해 준다.

name: Hold Hands
effect_entry: Does nothing.
effect_entry_ko: 같은 편 포켓몬끼리 손에 손을 잡는다. 굉장히 행복한 기분이 들게 된다.

name: Baby-Doll Eyes
effect_entry: Lowers the target's Attack by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 초롱초롱한 눈동자로 상대를 바라보며 공격을 떨어뜨린다. 반드시 선제공격할 수 있다.

name: Nuzzle
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Has a 100% chance to paralyze the target.
effect_entry_ko: 전기가 흐르는 볼을 비벼서 공격한다. 상대를 마비 상태로 만든다.

name: Hold Back
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Will not reduce the target's HP below 1.
effect_entry_ko: 적당히 공격하여 상대의 HP를 반드시 1은 남긴다.

name: Infestation
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. For the next 2–5 turns, the target cannot leave the field and is damaged for 1/16 its max HP at the end of each turn. The user continues to use other moves during this time. If the user leaves the field, this effect ends. Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use. rapid spin cancels this effect.
effect_entry_ko: 4-5턴 동안 상대에게 엉겨 붙어서 공격한다. 그동안 상대는 도망갈 수 없다.

name: Power-Up Punch
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Raises the user's Attack by one stage.
effect_entry_ko: 반복하여 때리면 점점 주먹이 단단해진다. 상대를 때리면 공격이 오른다.

name: Oblivion Wing
effect_entry: Deals regular damage. Drains 75% of the damage inflicted to heal the user.
effect_entry_ko: 조준한 상대로부터 HP를 흡수한다. 준 데미지의 반 이상 HP를 회복한다.

name: Thousand Arrows
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Grounds the target until it leaves battle. Ignores levitation effects and the immunity of flying-type Pokémon.
effect_entry_ko: 떠 있는 포켓몬도 맞힐 수 있다. 떠 있던 상대는 맞아서 땅에 떨어진다.

name: Thousand Waves
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Traps the target.
effect_entry_ko: 땅 위를 뻗어 나가는 파도로 공격한다. 파도에 휩쓸린 상대는 전투에서 도망칠 수 없게 된다.

name: Land's Wrath
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 대지의 힘을 모으고 그 힘을 상대에게 집중시켜서 데미지를 준다.

name: Light of Ruin
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. User takes 1/2 the damage it inflicts in recoil.
effect_entry_ko: 영원의 꽃의 파워를 빌려서 강력한 광선을 쏜다. 자신도 상당한 데미지를 입는다.

name: Origin Pulse
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 파랗게 빛나는 무수한 광선으로 상대를 공격한다.

name: Precipice Blades
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage.
effect_entry_ko: 대지의 힘을 칼날로 바꿔 상대를 공격한다.

name: Dragon Ascent
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage, then lowers the user's Defense and Special Defense by one stage each.
effect_entry_ko: 넓은 하늘에서 급속으로 강하하여 상대를 공격한다. 자신의 방어와 특수방어가 떨어진다.

name: Hyperspace Fury
effect_entry: Inflicts regular damage. Bypasses and removes any protection effect on the target.
effect_entry_ko: 많은 팔을 사용하여 방어와 판별을 무시하는 연속 공격이다. 자신의 방어가 떨어진다.
